stle.jp/", "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 34.665, "is_active": true, "longitude": 133.9355, "region_id": "jp_chugoku", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-01-23T02:44:39.52993+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "岡山城，岡山市中心的城堡，1597年建造。黑色外牆、金色屋頂，被稱為「烏城」。天守閣內展示岡山歷史、武具、甲冑。旭川旁，與後樂園隔河相望。春季櫻花、秋季紅葉最美。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Okayama Castle", "ticket_price": "成人500-700日圓", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 100, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-17:00（依季節調整）"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "09c33d17-3301-4483-967c-49f0107e610d", "fax": null, "name": "Churasun 6 沖繩", "tags": ["表演", "文化", "傳統", "晚餐秀"], "type": "experience", "notes": "", "phone": "", "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/workspace-files/attractions/1766560818892_zm98k2.png"], "address": "", "city_id": "naha", "website": "", "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 26.31, "is_active": true, "longitude": 127.76, "region_id": "jp_okinawa", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-20T12:18:04.29282+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "2024 年 5 月於那霸松山區開幕的全日最大規模表演俱樂部。其以華麗的燈光音效與專業舞者表演為特色，融合沖繩文化與現代娛樂，提供震撼視聽的感官饗宴，是那霸夜生活最受矚目的新地標。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Churasun 6 Okinawa", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 907, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": "https://share.google/vsYdzZRaZsVRGavzg", "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "09e5bd19-eca8-4b5e-83e1-8ba6f27ef1e8", "fax": null, "name": "慶州國立博物館", "tags": null, "type": "museum", "notes": "韓國古都，新羅王朝千年遺跡，佛國寺與石窟庵是世界遺產。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "gyeongju", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 35.8428, "is_active": true, "longitude": 129.2122, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:55:48.479558+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "慶州國立博物館，展示新羅王朝歷史文化。聖德大王神鐘、金冠、金帶、佛像都是國寶。雁鴨池出土文物、石窟庵複製品。這是認識新羅歷史的最佳場所，也是慶州必訪景點。免費參觀，建議預留2-3小時。可搭配雁鴨池、大陵苑一起遊覽。周一休館。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "Gyeongju National Museum", "ticket_price": "成人5000-10000韓元", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"closed": "週一", "tue_sun": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 480}, {"id": "0a3d441e-6cae-462e-bc34-ad0b158aa3af", "fax": null, "name": "素帖寺雙龍寺", "tags": ["聖山", "金塔", "信仰中心"], "type": "temple", "notes": "清邁必訪寺廟，306 階龍形階梯通往山頂，金色佛塔供奉佛舍利。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/0a3d441e-6cae-462e-bc34-ad0b158aa3af-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/0a3d441e-6cae-462e-bc34-ad0b158aa3af-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 18.8048, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.9219, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T06:50:00.630825+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《素帖寺雙龍寺》即 Wat Phra That Doi Suthep,清邁最重要的朝聖地。寺廟建於海拔1676公尺的素帖山頂,從山腳有306級階梯通往寺廟,兩側是七頭那伽龍神雕塑,故稱雙龍寺。金色佛塔供奉佛陀舍利,是泰北佛教的精神中心。清晨五點前往可避開人潮,薄霧中的金塔更顯神聖。寺廟平台可俯瞰整座清邁城,天氣晴朗時視野遼闊,雨季則雲霧繚繞如仙境。在地人相信來清邁若不登素帖寺,等於沒來過清邁。這不只是觀光名言,而是對信仰的尊重——這座寺廟,就是清邁的靈魂所在。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Wat Phra That Doi Suthep", "ticket_price": "成人30泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 549, "opening_hours": {"daily": "06:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "0a3d5598-4e86-469d-b80c-086fa27c5b4c", "fax": null, "name": "胡志明市設計街", "tags": ["設計街", "獨立品牌", "時尚"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "ho-chi-minh", "website": null, "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": 10.7751709, "is_active": true, "longitude": 106.6999907, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2026-04-04T11:19:47.295+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《胡志明市設計街》Le Thanh Ton Street 是新興的設計師聚集地,兩側是獨立品牌服飾店、工作室、咖啡館。越南年輕設計師在此展示作品,從時裝、飾品、家居用品到插畫都有。這裡的商品不便宜,但設計獨特,品質穩定。週末有設計市集,創作者親自擺攤。設計街代表胡志明的創意能量——不只是製造代工,也有原創設計。這是理解越南當代美學的窗口。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Le Thanh Ton Street", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "0a47d13c-a951-4f0b-bafb-9fc4a6f6570f", "fax": null, "name": "谷中銀座", "tags": ["下町", "商店街", "貓"], "type": "shopping", "notes": "日本最高檔購物區，百貨公司林立，周末步行者天國熱鬧非凡。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/0a47d13c-a951-4f0b-bafb-9fc4a6f6570f-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/0a47d13c-a951-4f0b-bafb-9fc4a6f6570f-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": 