, "name": "啟定皇陵", "tags": ["皇陵", "順化", "建築"], "type": "heritage", "notes": "中西合璧的獨特皇陵，有法式和越式混合風格。彩色玻璃和馬賽克裝飾華麗。門票150,000越盾。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "hue", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 16.4083, "is_active": true, "longitude": 107.5833, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:55:53.692429+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "順化啟定皇陵，阮朝皇帝啟定帝的陵墓，建於1920-1931年。融合越南、法國、中國建築風格，馬賽克、瓷器、彩繪玻璃，華麗精緻。這是順化必訪景點，也是阮朝陵墓中最特別的一座。門票150,000越南盾，建議預留1-2小時。可搭配嗣德皇陵、明命皇陵一起遊覽。需爬石階，穿好走的鞋。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Khai Dinh Tomb", "ticket_price": "成人150,000越南盾", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 586, "opening_hours": {"daily": "07:00-17:30"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "0d96ba9a-3a4a-4f32-bdc0-66a14601dd63", "fax": null, "name": "阿西爾傳統村落", "tags": ["文化", "傳統村落", "建築"], "type": "heritage", "notes": "保存傳統彩繪房屋的山區村落。Al Habala懸崖村可搭纜車前往。獨特的建築風格。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 18.2167, "is_active": true, "longitude": 42.5, "region_id": null, "country_id": "saudi_arabia", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:47.992608+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "阿西爾傳統村落，沙烏地阿拉伯景點，伊斯蘭聖地與現代化城市並存，展現阿拉伯文化與石油經濟發展。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "SA", "english_name": "Rijal Almaa Village", "ticket_price": "依官網而定", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"open": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "0da20d34-c880-4d74-be2d-dd13660b8556", "fax": null, "name": "銀飾工藝體驗", "tags": ["手作體驗", "銀飾", "工藝"], "type": "experience", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 18.7882778, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.9858802, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:49:11.714827+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《銀飾工藝體驗》在清邁老城區的小工作坊裡，師傅會教你用最傳統的方式敲打銀片。從融銀、塑形、拋光到鑲嵌，每個步驟都需要耐心與專注。你會理解為什麼手工銀飾比機器製品貴——不只是工時，而是每一次敲擊都帶著人的判斷與溫度。三小時的課程能完成一只簡單的戒指或手環，成品也許不完美，但那是你親手創造的。蘭納銀器的紋樣來自寺廟建築與自然圖騰，師傅會解釋每個符號的意義。這是用身體記憶理解工藝的方式。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Silver Jewelry Making", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "0da73ee9-1c55-4192-92e8-d6b1b4c6bfbf", "fax": null, "name": "DMM Kariyushi水族館", "tags": ["水族館", "科技", "親子", "室內"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "", "phone": "", "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/workspace-files/attractions/1766560902359_l57fhc.jpg"], "address": "", "city_id": "naha", "website": "", "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 26.175, "is_active": true, "longitude": 127.66, "region_id": "jp_okinawa", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-20T12:18:04.053746+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "沖繩DMM Kariyushi水族館，沖繩新興水族館，2020年開幕，位於豐見城。結合水族展示與數位藝術，投影、燈光、音樂營造夢幻氛圍。水母區、熱帶魚區、沖繩海洋生物都有展示。距那霸機場約15分鐘，適合雨天或最後一天行程。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "DMM Kariyushi Aquarium", "ticket_price": "免費或依業