330-f73e4f1155d3", "fax": null, "name": "姬路市立動物園", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/107a2a8f-3304-425a-8330-f73e4f1155d3-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/107a2a8f-3304-425a-8330-f73e4f1155d3-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "himeji", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 34.835, "is_active": true, "longitude": 134.695, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-01-23T02:48:38.075358+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "姬路市立動物園，位於姬路城內的動物園，1951年開園。大象、長頸鹿、企鵝、猴子等約120種動物。規模不大但交通便利，適合親子旅遊。這是姬路城參觀後的好去處，也是小朋友喜愛的地方。可搭配姬路城一起遊覽，門票有優惠套票。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Himeji City Zoo", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 100, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "10c5c33d-dfdf-4319-a57b-b80afdf0cd05", "fax": null, "name": "濟州黑豬肉一條街", "tags": ["美食", "黑豬肉", "烤肉", "濟州必吃", "特產"], "type": "food", "notes": "聚集多家黑豬肉烤肉店的美食街，黑豬肉是濟州特產。肉質鮮嫩無腥味，比一般豬肉香。推薦五花肉和排骨。配白切肉一起吃更道地。\n\n旅遊提示：排隊名店：多多烤肉、姑姑烤肉", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "jeju", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 33.4887737, "is_active": true, "longitude": 126.4987083, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2025-12-06T06:49:59.879559+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "濟州黑豬一條街，濟州市區烤黑豬肉餐廳聚集地。濟州黑豬肉質鮮嫩、油脂豐富，烤過後外酥內嫩，沾海鹽或泡菜一起吃。整條街都是烤肉店，競爭激烈價格合理。這是品嚐濟州黑豬肉的最佳場所，也是體驗韓式烤肉文化的好地方。建議選擇人潮多的店家，品質較有保障。晚餐時段