12-16T06:49:28.686827+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "羅托魯瓦，紐西蘭自然奇景，擁有壯麗山川與峽灣風光。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "NZ", "english_name": "Rotorua", "ticket_price": "依官網而定", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 855, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 480}, {"id": "16bf9a83-cdc6-459e-a602-a17016926455", "fax": null, "name": "鄭王廟", "tags": ["寺廟", "地標", "河景", "夕陽"], "type": "temple", "notes": "又稱黎明寺，五彩瓷片佛塔非常壯觀。可登塔俯瞰湄南河。夜間點燈很美。門票100泰銖。搭渡船前往。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "bangkok", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 13.7438976, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.4885137, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:37.064128+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《鄭王廟》又稱黎明寺(Wat Arun),矗立昭披耶河西岸,是曼谷最上鏡的寺廟。高棉式主塔高79公尺,外觀鑲嵌數百萬片彩色陶瓷和貝殼,在陽光下閃耀如寶石。夕陽時分最美,金色光芒灑在塔尖,對岸可拍攝黎明寺剪影與河面倒影。登塔階梯陡峭近70度,需手腳並用,但登頂後可360度俯瞰昭披耶河與曼谷舊城區,視野絕佳。夜間點燈後,塔身在燈光照射下更顯莊嚴夢幻。門票100泰銖,建議與大皇宮、臥佛寺安排同日參觀。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Wat Arun", "ticket_price": "成人100泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "1709f54c-030b-4e05-8d5b-0939f17d967e", "fax": null, "name": "烏魯瓦圖斷崖廟", "tags": ["寺廟", "懸崖", "日落", "克差舞", "壯觀"], "type": "temple", "notes": "建在70公尺高懸崖上的古老寺廟，俯瞰印度洋。日落時分景色絕美。每天18:00有傳統克差舞（Kecak Dance）表演，火舞配夕陽非常震撼。\n\n旅遊提示：一定要看克差舞，提早買票佔好位子", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "bali", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": -8.8291, "is_active": true, "longitude": 115.0849, "region_id": null, "country_id": "indonesia", "created_at": "2025-12-06T02:06:54.094592+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "烏魯瓦圖廟，峇里島最神聖的海崖寺廟之一，建在70公尺高的懸崖上。面向印度洋，日落時分景色震撼。傍晚有Kecak Fire Dance表演，火圈、舞蹈、吟唱，氣氛神秘。傍晚前往最佳。小心猴子會搶東西。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "ID", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "約Rp 50,000-200,000", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 527, "opening_hours": {"daily": "06:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "170b7d0d-b7c2-4e68-b650-4bef7f3b1705", "fax": null, "name": "瀨長島", "tags": ["網紅", "希臘風", "飛機", "沖繩"], "type": "shopping", "notes": "沖繩小希臘，白色階梯建築群。可看飛機起降。幸福鬆餅必吃。日落時分最美。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/170b7d0d-b7c2-4e68-b650-4bef7f3b1705-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/170b7d0d-b7c2-4e68-b650-4bef7f3b1705-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "naha", "website": null, "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": 26.1772, "is_active": true, "longitude": 127.6353, "region_id": "jp_okinawa", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:11:07.745058+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "沖繩瀨長島，那霸機場南方的小島，瀨長大橋連接本島。UmikajiTerrace、溫泉飯店、夕陽海景、飛機起降。免費通行，", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Senaga Island", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 853, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "17