_by": null, "description": "銀座小十，米其林三星壽司店，僅8席吧台座位。主廚奧田透被譽為壽司之神二郎的繼承者，技法傳統、食材極品。紅醋飯、熟成鮪魚、煮穴子都是招牌。這是東京最難預約的壽司店之一，也是壽司迷朝聖地。晚餐套餐約50,000-70,僅晚餐營業。需透過酒店或熟客介紹預約。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Ginza Kojyu", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "1b1eca7e-2df8-4755-8680-ae1993fe7cfc", "fax": null, "name": "萊利海灘", "tags": ["海灘", "攀岩", "喀比"], "type": "beach", "notes": "世界級攀岩勝地，只能搭船抵達的秘境海灘。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/1b1eca7e-2df8-4755-8680-ae1993fe7cfc-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/1b1eca7e-2df8-4755-8680-ae1993fe7cfc-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "krabi", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 8.0128, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.8375, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:55:51.767541+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《萊利海灘》僅能搭船抵達的絕美半島，被壯觀石灰岩懸崖環繞。分為東萊利和西萊利，西萊利日落景色絕美。此處是亞洲頂級攀岩聖地，吸引全球攀岩愛好者朝聖。附近有天然鑽石洞穴和公主洞可探索，11-4月乾季最適合造訪。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Railay Beach", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 240}, {"id": "1b2b7230-5f38-4473-820c-b8290d4207b4", "fax": null, "name": "原爆圓頂館", "tags": ["UNESCO", "歷史", "和平", "紀念"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "廣島和平的象徵，這座建築奇蹟般存留，提醒世人戰爭的殘酷與和平的可貴。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/1b2b7230-5f38-4473-820c-b8290d4207b4-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/1b2b7230-5f38-4473-820c-b8290d4207b4-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "hiroshima", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 34.3955, "is_active": true, "longitude": 132.4536, "region_id": "jp_chugoku", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-10-28T06:26:09.525838+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "1945年原子彈爆炸唯一留存的建築《原爆圓頂館》，殘破骨架訴說戰爭殘酷。UNESCO世界遺產，與和平紀念公園、紀念館一同警示世人珍惜和平，每年8月6日舉行追悼儀式。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Atomic Bomb Dome", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 2, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "1b400778-d9c6-4d5f-b912-aa7e4b87aea1", "fax": null, "name": "越前和紙手工造紙體驗", "tags": ["工藝體驗", "頂級體驗"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "頂級體驗 | 工藝體驗 | 價位: | 難度:None", "phone": null, "images": ["https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516631670063-e9c0f33afd06?w=800", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586864387634-92fda7c6cab8?w=800"], "address": null, "city_id": "osaka", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-04-06T22:24:08.033049+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "越前和紙有1500年歷史，是日本三大和紙之一，被指定為重要無形文化財。在福井縣越前市的紙漉き工房（大阪分工坊），跟隨人間國寶級紙漉き職人學習手工造紙。從楮樹皮處理、打漿、漉紙到乾燥，體驗完整的傳統造紙工序。學習「流し漉き」技法，製作獨一無二的手工和紙，可加入花瓣、金箔等裝飾。越前和紙被用於修復古書、製作高級書畫用紙，是日本文化的重要載體。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Echizen Washi Papermaking 