0度高溫燒製。完成一個銀質首飾盒或碗，表面覆蓋華麗的五彩珐瑯。Benjarong圖案包括「克拉通」花朵、「那迦」神獸等泰國傳統元素。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Bangkok Benjarong Enamel Silver Crafting", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 0}, {"id": "1d8badb5-22ee-4a33-9f34-77c8e186cc91", "fax": null, "name": "公主港地下河", "tags": ["世界遺產", "地下河", "洞穴", "鐘乳石", "巴拉望"], "type": "heritage", "notes": "世界新七大自然奇觀之一，全長8.2公里的可航行地下河，穿越石灰岩洞穴系統。需提前預約門票，遊船約45分鐘，可見壯觀的鐘乳石和石筍。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "palawan", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 9.75, "is_active": true, "longitude": 118.75, "region_id": null, "country_id": "philippines", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:07:07.163666+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "公主港地下河，UNESCO世界自然遺產，世界最長可航行地下河之一。搭船進入石灰岩洞穴，鐘乳石、石筍、蝙蝠、燕子，景色夢幻。這是巴拉望必訪景點，也是菲律賓代表景觀。門票約1,500披索，需提前預訂許可。建議預留一整天。可搭配薩邦海灘一起遊覽。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "PH", "english_name": "Puerto Princesa Underground River", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 90, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 240}, {"id": "1d9f50a0-c7e6-4bd4-aa4d-7f7b15b39e55", "fax": null, "name": "第一郡步行街", "tags": ["步行街", "現代", "夜景", "噴泉"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "ho-chi-minh", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 10.7737196, "is_active": true, "longitude": 106.7040457, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2025-10-28T06:43:07.039598+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated