的建築群,金碧輝煌到近乎炫目。翡翠玉佛寺位於宮殿內,供奉著一尊用整塊翡翠雕成的佛像,泰國國王每年會親自為其更換三季法衣。宮牆上的馬賽克磚片拼貼出《羅摩衍那》的史詩場景,每一片都是手工鑲嵌。遊客眾多,規定嚴格:短褲背心禁止入內,拍照不能背對佛像。這是一場視覺的過載,也是權力美學的極致展示。離開時你會感到疲憊,不只是因為炎熱,而是因為這種華麗需要大量的注意力去消化。這是曼谷的官方門面,也是最不日常的曼谷。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Grand Palace", "ticket_price": "成人500泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 1, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:30-15:30（最後售票15:00）"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 150}, {"id": "1e54c905-dfbd-4556-bcbd-6f0f384aefc4", "fax": null, "name": "普吉老城", "tags": ["老城", "建築", "普吉島", "文青"], "type": "heritage", "notes": "中葡混血Sino-Portuguese建築很有特色。彩色房屋很好拍。週日有Walking Street夜市。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/1e54c905-dfbd-4556-bcbd-6f0f384aefc4-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/1e54c905-dfbd-4556-bcbd-6f0f384aefc4-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "phuket", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 7.8847774, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.3892206, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:11:11.606113+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "普吉老城區保留了19世紀中葡混合建築風格，彩色Sino-Portuguese建築沿街排列。塔朗路和迪布路最具代表性，咖啡廳、藝廊和精品店林立，週日有步行街市集。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Phuket Old Town", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 639, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "1e6933d7-4fd3-42e0-b1e7-abe560bf43c7", "fax": null, "name": "普達措國家公園", "tags": ["國家公園", "高原", "湖泊", "香格里拉"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "門票含環保車，旺