3800108.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940"], "address": null, "city_id": "aso", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 32.8331, "is_active": true, "longitude": 131.1667, "region_id": "jp_kyushu", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-16T06:38:10.442072+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "熊本上色見熊野座神社，隱藏在山林中的神社，參道100多座鳥居綿延山坡。苔蘚覆蓋石階、杉木林蔭蔽天，充滿神秘氛圍。動漫《螢火之森》取景地。這是熊本秘境神社，也是攝影愛好者天堂。免費參觀，建議早上前往，光線最美。需自駕前往，距熊本市區約1.5小時。可搭配高千穗峽一起遊覽。階梯陡峭，需穿著舒適鞋子。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Kamishikimi Kumanoimasu Shrine", "ticket_price": "免費或300-500日圓", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 29, "opening_hours": {"daily": "06:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 45}, {"id": "1f2a187d-fe31-4e4a-81ef-6715a33db21f", "fax": null, "name": "迦南島", "tags": ["竹籃船", "體驗", "水鄉", "趣味"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "hoi-an", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 15.8795863, "is_active": true, "longitude": 108.3319406, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2025-10-28T08:35:27.15843+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "會安迦南島，會安外海的椰林水道生態區。搭籃船穿越水椰林，船夫表演旋轉籃船、釣螃蟹，刺激又好玩。這是會安必體驗活動，也是親子旅遊首選。半日遊約300,000-500,000越南盾。需穿可弄濕的衣物。會濕身，很好玩。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Cam Thanh Coconut Village", "ticket_price": "依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 8, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "1f58428f-fe37-4741-a209-e52105d29928",