ll, "description": "福岡中洲屋台街，中洲地區的屋台聚集地。拉麵、關東煮、燒鳥、炒麵，博多美食應有盡有。屋台僅5-10席座位，與老闆、鄰座客人聊天，充滿人情味。這是福岡夜晚必體驗活動，也是認識博多飲食文化的窗口。一餐約1,500-3,000日圓，建議晚上8點後前往。可搭配中洲川端商店街、博多運河城一起遊覽。注意營業到午夜，部分店家不定休。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Nakasu Yatai", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "21b7ee2f-bd27-4a74-8ea0-f2b4db34744d", "fax": null, "name": "寶妮小馬俱樂部", "tags": ["親子", "動物", "體驗", "戶外"], "type": "體驗活動", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/21b7ee2f-bd27-4a74-8ea0-f2b4db34744d-1.jpg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/21b7ee2f-bd27-4a74-8ea0-f2b4db34744d-2.jpg"], "address": null, "city_id": "pattaya", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 12.9534601, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.9382965, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2026-03-29T11:41:07.097722+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《寶妮小馬俱樂部》是芭達雅郊區的家庭式馬場，提供小型馬（Pony）騎乘體驗，特別適合兒童。除了騎馬課程，還有餵食、梳理馬匹的互動活動。園區環境整潔，教練親切專業，強調動物福利。對於初次接觸馬術的孩子，這裡是最溫和的入門選擇，也是親子旅遊的溫馨記憶。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Pipo Pony Club", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": "09:00-17:00", "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "21cd6583-885a-4023-9237-755f8796e86e", "fax": null, "name": "海神廟", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "bali", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": -8.6215, "is_active": true, "longitude": 115.0866, "region_id": null, "country_id": "indonesia", "created_at": "2026-01-23T22:33:54.847595+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "峇里島海神廟，峇里島最有名的海上廟宇，建在海中岩石上。漲潮時廟與陸地分離，落潮時可步行前往。日落時分，廟宇剪影與海景，景色震撼。傍晚前往看日落最佳。潮汐時間需注意。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "ID", "english_name": "Tanah Lot Temple", "ticket_price": "約Rp 50,000-200,000", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 100, "opening_hours": {"daily": "06:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "21d16adb-b62d-467d-b4a4-d93a8edf89f5", "fax": null, "name": "班努爾島", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "palawan", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 11.96, "is_active": true, "longitude": 120.18, "region_id": null, "country_id": "philippines", "created_at": "2026-01-24T09:04:19.780908+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "宿霧班努爾島，宿霧北部的離島，以潔白沙灘、清澈海水、悠閒氛圍聞名。可游泳、浮潛、看日落、吃海鮮、騎摩托車環島。這是宿霧必訪景點，也是避開人潮的好選擇。住宿約1,000-5,000披索/晚。建議停留2-3天。從宿霧搭巴士+渡輪約4小時。可搭配 Malapascua Island 一起遊覽。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "PH", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "21f25d9a-83bf-4d95-85a3-c77d9dd3014d", "fax": null, "name": "備前燒陶藝體驗", "tags": ["陶藝", "DIY", "職人", "傳統工藝"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "體驗日本六古窯之一的備前燒製作，作品需約1個月後取件或郵寄", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/stor