d_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《泰拳體驗課》在傳統拳館或健身房都能找到,但氛圍差異極大。傳統拳館保留祭拜儀式與師徒制度,訓練強度高且不遷就初學者。課程從纏手布、基本站姿開始,學習直拳、肘擊、膝撞與低掃踢。對著沙包反覆練習時,你會理解泰拳的力量來自腰跨轉動而非手臂肌肉。汗水、皮革氣味與傳統音樂營造出獨特氛圍。這不是溫和的文化體驗,而是真實的體能挑戰,隔天全身痠痛是必然結果。但在疼痛中,你觸碰到了泰國武術哲學的邊緣——尊重、紀律與身體覺知。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Muay Thai Class", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "2549f07d-dedd-439b-9b1c-8a32fd7181b8", "fax": null, "name": "吉安慶修院", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "花蓮縣吉安鄉中興路345-1號", "city_id": "769364e9-d3e2-474f-bc80-0184c00e6d9e", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 23.9614, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.5672, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-01-09T03:43:44.063392+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "花蓮吉安的日式寺院，建於1917年。木造建築、日式庭園，充滿禪意。這是台灣保存最完整的日式寺院之一，見證了日治時期的移民歷史。寺院不大，但環境清幽，是花蓮重要的文化資產。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": "Yoshino Shingon Mission", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 69, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:30-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 30}, {"id": "254e3f7a-2873-4539-96e7-104876007c96", "fax": null, "name": "波之上海灘", "tags": null, "type": "beach", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/254e3f7a-2873-4539-96e7-104876007c96-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpg