: true, "longitude": 99.936, "region_id": "th_central", "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2026-03-17T03:14:01.620413+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "山洞中的皇室行宮，陽光透過洞頂的開口照射進來，形成壯觀的光柱。行宮在光影中顯得格外神聖，這是大自然與人文建築最完美的結合。清晨時分，光線最美，但需要健行約30分鐘才能抵達這處秘境。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Phraya Nakhon Cave", "ticket_price": "國家公園門票200泰銖（含Phraya Nakhon Cave）", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "需配合潮汐，建議07:00-11:00前往"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "269189c5-5b03-479c-a64c-4a40ddbe56c2", "fax": null, "name": "元伊勢籠神社", "tags": ["c"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "", "phone": "", "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/workspace-files/attractions/1766993391908_fr8897.jpg"], "address": "京都府宮津市大垣430", "city_id": "kyoto", "website": "", "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 35.5739, "is_active": true, "longitude": 135.1817, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-18T08:31:13.414513+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "丹後地區地位最高、最古老、最重要的神社。相傳伊勢神宮祭祀的天照大神與豐受大神曾遷徙至此，故被尊稱為伊勢神宮之本源。其本殿欄杆裝飾著全日僅此兩處獲准使用的「五色座玉」，展現莊嚴神聖的歷史地位。後方奧宮真名井神社則以古老能量與神聖湧水著稱。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Moto-Ise Kono Shrine", "ticket_price": "免費或300-500日圓", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 87, "opening_hours": {"daily": "06:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "26adbab5-753d-4ece-8374-b9352e9981a5", "fax": null, "name": "首爾高麗青瓷燒製工坊", "tags": ["工藝體驗", "頂級體驗"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "頂級體驗 | 工藝體驗 | 價位: | 難度:None", "phone": null, "images": ["https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1610701596007-11502861dcfa?w=800", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565193566173-7a0ee3dbe261?w=800"], "address": null, "city_id": "seoul", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2026-04-06T22:24:09.203005+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "高麗青瓷是韓國最引以為傲的陶瓷藝術，以翠綠色「秘色」釉和精緻的鑲嵌技法聞名，在12世紀達到巔峰。在首爾仁寺洞的傳統窯坊，跟隨國家無形文化財保持者學習青瓷製作。使用高麗時代傳承下來的配方釉藥，學習拉坯、鑲嵌（象嵌）技法。在器物表面雕刻紋樣後，嵌入白土或黑土，再施青瓷釉，經1250度還原焰燒製，呈現獨特的「翡色」釉面。完成作品如茶碗、香爐或梅瓶。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "Seoul Goryeo Celadon Pottery Workshop", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 0}, {"id": "26b40493-ecab-4bb3-830b-b50d6c9aeaa4", "fax": null, "name": "安平老街", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://wzvwmawpkapcmkfmkvav.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/resources/attractions/26b40493-ecab-4bb3-830b-b50d6c9aeaa4/1776736993749_7202i2y7pmn.jpg"], "address": "", "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-04-21T01:56:58.009057+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-21T02:03:23.718046+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "300 多年前荷蘭人在此興建的第一條街道，擁有「台灣第一街」之美稱。老街以延平街為主軸，街道兩旁不僅有許多具歷史感的舊式建築，更集結了各式古早味童玩、特色小吃與百年蜜餞行，是台南旅遊的必訪景點。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-