"created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《松瓦路》Song Wat Road 是清邁古城東側的老街區,保留了百年木造老宅與華人建築。這裡不是觀光熱點,而是在地生活的延續——老咖啡館、雜貨店、裁縫鋪與現代咖啡館、藝廊、設計旅店共存。清晨時分老人在路邊喝咖啡聊天,午後陽光將木造房屋的影子投在石板路上。近年文創工作者進駐,開設選物店與工作室,但沒有刻意趕走原有居民。這是清邁正在發生的變化——新與舊的協商、傳統與創新的平衡。沿著松瓦路散步,你會看到時間的多層次並存:百年老宅、八零年代店面、當代設計空間,在同一條街上呼吸。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Song Wat Road", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 366, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "2ceb0f40-380a-4e78-9817-dbc2beb3bc12", "fax": null, "name": "亞庇市立清真寺", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "sabah", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 5.9812, "is_active": true, "longitude": 116.0712, "region_id": null, "country_id": "malaysia", "created_at": "2026-01-23T22:34:03.936725+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "亞庇市立清真寺，亞庇最美的水上清真寺，建於2000年。藍白色圓頂建築矗立在人工湖上，倒映水面如浮在水上。可容納12,000人，是沙巴第二大清真寺。這是亞庇地標，也是拍照熱門景點。非穆斯林可參觀，建議傍晚前往，夕陽時分最美。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "MY", "english_name": "Kota Kinabalu City Mosque", "ticket_price": "免費（外觀參觀）", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 100, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00（祈禱時間不開放）"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "2cf98aca-edb2-4521-8d88-9d1e1e0638e1", "fax": null, "name": "瑤琴夜市", "tags": ["夜市", "小吃", "夜生活"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 30.