賽。這是日本職棒聖地，也是體驗日本棒球文化的好地方。建議提前購票。周邊有東京巨蛋城、LaQua溫泉、遊樂設施。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Tokyo Dome", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "31205778-6d8d-43bb-9508-7abfda634176", "fax": null, "name": "哥拉巴園", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/31205778-6d8d-43bb-9508-7abfda634176-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/31205778-6d8d-43bb-9508-7abfda634176-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "nagasaki", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 32.7333, "is_active": true, "longitude": 129.8647, "region_id": "jp_kyushu", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-01-23T00:36:41.447801+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "長崎哥拉巴園，長崎山腰的洋館群，展示明治時代外國商人住宅。哥拉巴宅邸、蝴蝶夫人舞台、長崎港景觀。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Glover Garden", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 1, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "3123c0e8-eb31-4b07-b91f-b63a513b5122", "fax": null, "name": "札幌時計台", "tags": ["歷史", "地標", "拍照"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "札幌的象徵，1878年建造的美式木造建築。每小時整點報時，是北海道開拓時代的歷史見證，內部展示時鐘機械。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/3123c0e8-eb31-4b07-b91f-b63a513b5122-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/3123c0e8-eb31-4b07-b91f-b63a513b5122-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "sapporo", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 43.0631, "is_active": true, "longitude": 141.3536, "region_id": "jp_hokkaido", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-11-01T12:55:05.003965+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "札幌時計台，札幌地標，建於1878年，北海道最古老的木造建築之一。美國風格鐘樓、白色外牆、紅色屋頂，是札幌象徵。內部展示札幌開拓史、時鐘機械構造。這是札幌必拍景點，雖然規模不大，但歷史意義重大。建議快速參觀拍照。位於札幌市中心，夜晚點燈後更顯優雅。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Sapporo Clock Tower", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 45}, {"id": "3129f041-e237-44b9-9ddf-ef582ecde4fd", "fax": null, "name": "金融塔", "tags": ["摩天樓", "觀景台", "夜景"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "ho-chi-minh", "website": null, "category": "地標建築 / Landmark", "latitude": 10.7718634, "is_active": true, "longitude": 106.7044633, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2026-04-04T11:19:45.601+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《金融塔》Bitexco Financial Tower 高262公尺,是胡志明最高建築之一。49樓觀景台(Saigon Skydeck)可360度俯瞰城市,白天看城市紋理,夜晚看萬家燈火。建築外型設計靈感來自蓮花,越南國花的象徵。觀景台門票約台幣600元,包含飲料。建議黃昏前往,可以同時看到日景與夜景。這座大樓代表胡志明的野心——從戰爭廢墟中重建,成為東南亞經濟中心。站在高處俯瞰,你會理解這座城市的活力從何而來。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Bitexco Financial Tower", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "3138814e-2553-4372-afe2-a494c0842cc8", "fax": null, "name": "八甲田山", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/3138814e-2553-4372-afe2-a494c0842cc8-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/3138814e-2553-4372-afe2-a494c0842cc8-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "aomori", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 40.66, "is_active": true, "longitude": 140.88, "region_id": "jp_tohoku", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-01-23T02:48:50.219344+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "青森八甲田山，青森南部的火山群，主峰大岳海拔1,584公尺。夏季登山健行、冬季滑雪樹冰，四季活動豐富。八甲田纜車可達山頂，俯瞰青森市區與陸奧灣。這是青森代表山岳，也是東北登山勝地。纜車往返2,建議秋天紅葉季前往。冬季樹冰壯觀，但需注意保暖。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Mt. Hakkoda", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 100, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "31398d91-3fce-42eb-84ff-da5dac467f8d", "fax": null, "name": "西芳寺（苔寺）", "tags": ["苔蘚", "庭園", "預約制"], "type": "temple", "notes": "苔寺，120 種苔蘚覆蓋庭園，參拜需事前申請抄經。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/31398d91-3fce-42eb-84ff-da5dac467f8d-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/31398d91-3fce-42eb-84ff-da5dac467f8d-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "kyoto", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 34.9917, "is_active": true, "longitude": 135.685, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-06T06:57:29.26525+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "