ion": "三亞艾迪遜酒店，位於海棠灣，設計融合現代奢華與熱帶風情。無邊際泳池面向大海，房間寬敞明亮，服務細緻周到。酒店有多間餐廳，提供國際美食。適合蜜月、家庭度假，價格中高端。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "CN", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "房價約2500-6000元/晚起", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 24, "opening_hours": {"daily": "24小時服務"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 1440}, {"id": "317f4246-3cfc-4448-abe5-86aaf66374b7", "fax": null, "name": "伊根舟屋", "tags": [], "type": "attraction", "notes": "", "phone": "", "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/workspace-files/attractions/1766995006213_udbd5t.jpg"], "address": "京都府與謝郡伊根町", "city_id": "kyoto", "website": "", "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 35.6758, "is_active": true, "longitude": 135.2817, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-18T08:31:13.090718+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "位於京都丹後半島的伊根舟屋是日本最具特色的水上建築群，擁有超過一千七百年的歷史。獨特的兩層樓結構將一樓設計為停泊船隻與存放漁具的船庫，二樓則作為生活起居室。這種緊鄰海面、排山倒海而建的景觀被譽為日本威尼斯。現存兩百多間舟屋不僅展現了漁民與海共生的智慧，更被指定為日本重要傳統建築物群保存地區。有「海上京都」之稱。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Ine Funaya", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 212, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "31b2773f-4781-4b47-a562-e15790f5e417", "fax": null, "name": "長崎新地中華街", "tags": ["中華街", "美食", "長崎"], "type": "food", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/31b2773f-4781-4b47-a562-e15790f5e417-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/31b2773f-4781-4b47-a562-e15790f5e417-2.jpeg"], "address": nul