，穿越千年杉木林、越過山嶺、渡過溪流。沿途參拜王子社（休息點神社），淨化身心。夜宿古道旁的溫泉旅館，享受療癒的溫泉浴。早晚進行森林冥想與瑜伽，聆聽自然的聲音。由熊野修驗道的山伏（修行者）帶領，講解神道與自然崇拜。這是結合自然、靈性、身體鍛鍊的療癒之旅。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Kumano Kodo Spiritual Pilgrimage 5 Days", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 0}, {"id": "3a8d8f37-c466-49d0-9b6b-e4f3741c22f6", "fax": null, "name": "松園別館", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "花蓮縣花蓮市松園街65號", "city_id": "769364e9-d3e2-474f-bc80-0184c00e6d9e", "website": "https://www.pinegarden.com.tw/", "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 23.9783, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.6103, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-01-09T03:43:44.063392+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "花蓮的日治時期建築群，建於1913年，是花蓮港兵事部辦公室。松樹環繞的日式庭園，寧靜而優雅。現在是藝文展覽空間，保留了歷史建築的原貌。站在松園別館的觀景台，可以俯瞰花蓮港和太平洋，視野開闊。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": "Pine Garden", "ticket_price": "全票60元", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 65, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "3a938c67-f838-4fef-b996-ebad7eaf9f33", "fax": null, "name": "影島大橋", "tags": ["大橋", "開橋秀", "歷史", "拍照", "特色"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "韓國唯一的開啟橋，每日14:00會開橋15分鐘讓船隻通過。1934年建造，見證釜山近代史。電影《國際市場》重要場景。開橋時刻是獨特的觀光體驗。\n\n旅遊提示：13:45到達橋邊等待開橋最佳位置", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "busan", "website": null, "category": "地標建築 / Landmark", "latitude": 35.093, "is_active": true, "longitude": 129.039, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:01:12.282504+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "釜山影島大橋，釜山第一座跨海大橋，1934年建成。橋身每天中午會升起，讓船隻通過，是釜山獨特景觀。橋上有影島大橋展望台。這是釜山歷史地標，也是看釜山港的好地方。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "Yeongdo Bridge", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 772, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-20:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 30}, {"id": "3aa8f057-1f9c-4ca2-aa5e-7f31e5ec538e", "fax": null, "name": "文殊院", "tags": ["佛寺", "祈福", "紅牆打卡", "小吃", "當地人推薦"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "門口小吃比景區內更道地", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "成都市青羊區文殊院街66號", "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 30.6772, "is_active": true, "longitude": 104.0628, "region_id": "cn_southwest", "country_id": "china", "created_at": "2025-12-05T14:34:23.081288+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "成都香火最旺的佛教寺院，據說祈求學業、事業特別靈驗。免費領香，紅牆是網紅打卡點，常見新人拍婚紗。寺外小吃街是當地人最愛，文殊院豆湯飯、甜水面、張涼粉等，比錦里寬窄巷子更接地氣。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "CN", "english_name": "Wenshu Monastery", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 10, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:30-17:30"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "3abe1ea6-260e-428c-88c0-f2db24f64c6a", "fax": null, "name": "Jomtien Beach", "tags": ["海灘", "水上活動", "悠閒", "日落"], "type": "海灘", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/3abe1ea6-260e-428c-88c0-f2db24f64c6a-1.jpg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/3a