07+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "CộngCàPhê，胡志明市復古風格咖啡廳連鎖店，以共產主義風格裝潢聞名。復古海報、標語、老物件、綠色軍裝營造懷舊氛圍。椰子咖啡是招牌，椰奶混合咖啡，香甜滑順。價格親民，是越南年輕人聚會地。這是體驗越南咖啡文化的熱門地點，也是拍照打卡的好地方。多家分店，第一郡、第三郡都有。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Cong Caphe", "ticket_price": "約30,000-50,000越南盾/杯", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 909, "opening_hours": {"daily": "07:00-23:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "4ca8719f-1d4d-4227-bcc8-dce1145a263f", "fax": null, "name": "帕辛寺", "tags": ["皇家寺廟", "蘭納建築", "壁畫"], "type": "temple", "notes": "位於古城內西邊。潑水節期間非常熱鬧。可與其他古城寺廟一起安排。免費入場但可隨喜捐獻。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/4ca8719f-1d4d-4227-bcc8-dce1145a263f-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/4ca8719f-1d4d-4227-bcc8-dce1145a263f-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 18.7883, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.9817, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T08:00:05.846366+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《帕辛寺》Wat Phra Singh 是清邁古城內最重要的寺廟之一,供奉著Phra Singh佛像。主殿的蘭納式建築保存完整,多層屋簷、金色裝飾、精緻木雕,是泰北建築美學的代表作。殿內壁畫描繪19世紀清邁的日常生活場景,從市集交易到宮廷宴會,是珍貴的歷史圖像紀錄。每年潑水節期間,Phra Singh佛像會被請出遊行,吸引大批信眾朝聖。平日前往,可以看到僧侶在寺內誦經、學習,這是活著的宗教空間,不只是觀光景點。建議清晨或傍晚前往,避開旅行團,感受寺廟本該有的寧靜。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "成人100-200泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 335, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "4cc52d95-26d5-4b5e-8a3a-05718177e7bc", "fax": null