c/attractions/thailand/4e496d29-22de-4870-8949-645c994a7bb9-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 18.7871427, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.986784, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:38.983953+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《柴迪隆寺》即契迪龍寺 Wat Chedi Luang,是清邁古城內最具歷史重量的寺廟。建於1391年的佛塔曾高達82公尺,1545年地震後崩塌至目前的60公尺。泰國政府曾考慮修復,但最終決定保留殘缺狀態——因為這份不完整,本身就是歷史的見證。四面巨象托舉塔身的設計,是蘭納建築的經典元素。清晨時分僧侶在此誦經,聲音在古老空間中迴盪,莊嚴肅穆。黃昏時夕陽將塔身染成金色,是攝影愛好者最愛的時刻。這座寺廟教會我們:有些東西,不需要修復到完美,殘缺也是一種美。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Wat Chedi Luang", "ticket_price": "成人100-200泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "4e7976c4-ae94-430b-88ff-16e9962a1ff3", "fax": null, "name": "福岡麵包超人博物館", "tags": ["親子", "麵包超人", "博物館"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "福岡的麵包超人主題樂園，適合親子同遊。遊樂設施和餐廳都以麵包超人為主題。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/4e7976c4-ae94-430b-88ff-16e9962a1ff3-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/4e7976c4-ae94-430b-88ff-16e9962a1ff3-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "fukuoka", "website": null, "category": "主題樂園 / Theme Park", "latitude": 33.5886, "is_active": true, "longitude": 130.4014, "region_id": "jp_kyushu", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-12T05:45:46.050091+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "福岡麵包超人博物館，親子主題博物館，展示麵包超人世界。麵包超人劇場、遊樂設施、周邊商店、麵包工坊應有盡有。小朋友可以與麵包超人合照、玩遊樂設施。這是福岡親子旅遊首選，也是麵包超人迷天堂。位於福岡市區，交通方便。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Fukuoka Anpanman Museum", "ticket_price": "成人500-1000日圓", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 752, "opening_hours": {"closed": "週一", "tue_sun": "09:30-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "4e8c807d-4894-464b-983e-2532d6ccf720", "fax": null, "name": "清水斷崖", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": "Su花公路著名景點，建議在和仁或崇德停車場觀景，拍照注意安全", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "花蓮縣秀林鄉蘇花公路", "city_id": "769364e9-d3e2-474f-bc80-0184c00e6d9e", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 24.185, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.698, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-01-09T03:36:28.944514+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "蘇花公路上最壯觀的景色，斷崖從海拔800公尺垂直落入太平洋。公路緊貼著山壁開鑿，一邊是峭壁，一邊是深淵。這段路驚險刺激，但風景絕美。天氣好時，海水呈現深淺不一的藍綠色，令人屏息。這是台灣八景之一，也是環島必經的景觀大道。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": "Qingshui Cliff", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 32, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 30}, {"id": "4ecb70b5-2632-486f-a756-7ec639ddd67a", "fax": null, "name": "天門山", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": "張家界的著名景區，天門洞是世界最高天然穿山溶洞。玻璃棧道和世界最長纜車是亮點。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 29.05, "is_active": true, "longitude": 110.4833, "region_id": null, "country_id": "china", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:51.568803+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "天門山，中國名山，自然風光優美，歷史文化深厚，是登山朝聖勝地。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "CN", "english_name": "Tianmen Mountain", "ticket_price": "成人50-150元", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "06:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "4ee1e05b-4f0d-4c68-92ff-3d4dfb88e50a", "fax": null, "name": "Innisfree濟州小屋", "tags": ["購物", "體驗", "化妝品", "K-beauty"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "Innisfree品牌體驗空間，有濟州島主題展示和化妝品購物", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": "https://www.innisfree.com/", "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": 33.3085, "is_active": true, "longitude": 126.2915, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2026-03-17T03:14:48.14169+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "濟州島Innisfree濟州小屋，韓國化妝品品牌Innisfree的品牌體驗空間。展示濟州島主題的產品、火山泥面膜DIY體驗、濟州植物萃取過程。空間設計融入濟州島元素，石牆、綠植、火山岩。咖啡廳提供濟州綠茶飲品。除了購物，也能了解品牌如何結合濟州島的自然資源。這是Innisfree粉絲必訪之地，也是體驗韓國化妝品文化的好地方。免費參觀。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "Innisfree Jeju House", "ticket_price": "免費入場", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "4ef8f902-d3d6-4291-ba08-cac4c0350b38", "fax": null, "name": "小琉球遊客中心", "tags": ["遊客中心", "環保教育", "資訊"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": "https://www.pthg.gov.tw/", "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 22.3445, "is_active": true, "longitude": 120.3732, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-03-17T03:12:44.571464+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "小琉球旅遊資訊的核心據點。除了提供旅遊諮詢，這裡也有「不塑之島」的環保教育展示，說明小琉球如何從塑膠氾濫轉型為環保示範島。認識小琉球的永續旅遊理念，從這裡開始。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": "Xiaoliuqiu Visitor Center", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:30-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 30}, {"id": "4f0d77bd-bb3b-48b4-b743-d3d520be840b", "fax": null, "name": "首爾傳統市場商人體驗", "tags": ["在地深度", "頂級體驗"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "頂級體驗 | 在地深度 | 價位: | 難度:None", "phone": null, "images": ["https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517154421773-0529f29ea451?w=800", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509042239860-f550ce710b93?w=800"], "address": null, "city_id": "seoul", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2026-04-06T22:24:12.645806+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "在首爾最熱鬧的廣藏市場，跟隨經營三代的攤販家族體驗一日商人生活。清晨6點抵達市場，幫忙攤位準備工作：擺放商品、調配醬料、蒸煮年糕。學習韓國小吃製作：綠豆煎餅（빈대떡）、辣炒年糕（떡볶이）、血腸（순대）。最重要的是學習叫賣技巧：如何用韓語招攬客人、議價、介紹商品。親自站在攤位前販售，體驗與客人互動的樂趣。午餐品嚐市場各攤位的美食，每個攤主都會招待一點自家特色。下午學習韓國傳統醃製泡菜，並打包一罐回家。這是最道地的首爾基層生活體驗。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "Seoul Traditional Market Vendor Experience", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 0}, {"id": "4f250c2a-1bcf-4efe-8525-435711cba549", "fax": null, "name": "沙壩梯田", "tags": ["自然", "梯田", "山區", "必去"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "越南最壯觀梯田風光，少數民族村落健行，晨霧雲海絕美。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "sapa", "website": null, "catego