訪景點，也是認識華人移民歷史的好地方。門票120,000越南盾，建議預留30分鐘-1小時。可搭配日本橋、潮州會館一起遊覽。需脫鞋進入。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Fujian Assembly Hall", "ticket_price": "含於會安古鎮通票", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 45}, {"id": "4fbbce78-cd27-456e-b03f-fba9e7e78f69", "fax": null, "name": "會安傳統刺繡與奧黛訂製", "tags": ["工藝體驗", "頂級體驗"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "頂級體驗 | 工藝體驗 | 價位: | 難度:None", "phone": null, "images": ["https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591337676887-a217a6970a8a?w=800", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1601925260368-ae2f83cf8b7f?w=800"], "address": null, "city_id": "hoi-an", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2026-04-06T22:24:08.586502+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "會安是越南傳統刺繡與服飾製作的中心，擁有數百年歷史。在會安古城的刺繡工坊，跟隨越南刺繡大師學習傳統刺繡技法。使用絲線繡製越南經典圖案：蓮花、鳳凰、竹子、梅花。學習平繡、盤金繡、結繡等技法，完成一幅刺繡作品或奧黛袖口裝飾。可選配訂製一套完整奧黛（越南傳統長衫），使用絲綢或亞麻，手工刺繡裝飾，量身訂製，需3-5天完成。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Hoi An Traditional Embroidery & Ao Dai Tailoring", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 0}, {"id": "4ff99b1b-765b-4796-830f-f907d8977226", "fax": null, "name": "淡水老街", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "新北市淡水區中正路", "city_id": "newtaipei-e314eae7-27b1-42f4-a26e-fdcc7b1bcaf7", "website": null, "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": 25.1692, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.4387, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-01-09T03:31:23.908376+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "新北市淡水老街，淡水河畔的歷史街區。紅毛城、淡水禮拜堂、滬尾砲台，見證了西班牙、荷蘭、清代、日治的歷史。老街上阿給、魚丸、鐵蛋是必吃美食。傍晚時分，在河岸散步，看夕陽將淡水河染成金黃，是淡水最浪漫的時刻。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": "Tamsui Old Street", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 13, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放，商店約10:00-21:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 150}, {"id": "50132c20-3b09-46c2-b4fc-06eb1117ec41", "fax": null, "name": "Mosu Seoul", "tags": null, "type": "food", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "seoul", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 37.5666791, "is_active": true, "longitude": 126.9782914, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:49:08.280159+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "首爾Mosu Seoul，米其林三星餐廳。主廚安成재曾在Noma、Eleven Madison Park工作，將北歐料理哲學帶回韓國。使用韓國當季食材，以發酵、熟成技法處理，呈現韓國風土。品嚐套餐約15-18道菜，每道菜都是藝術。這是韓國最頂級的Fine Dining餐廳，也是米其林迷必訪之地。價格高昂，需提前數月預約。適合特殊慶祝場合。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "Mosu Seoul", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-20:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "5036230b-49be-4be1-8d1e-c14cd6457b60", "fax": null, "name": "KidZania 福岡", "tags": ["親子", "職業體驗", "室內"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "福岡的兒童職業體驗樂園，可體驗各種職業。警察、消防員、飛機駕駛等，寓教於樂。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://images.pexels.com/photos/3048516/pexels-photo-3048516.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=