 "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 13.7524938, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.4935089, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T08:00:05.245609+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《Jodd Fairs 夜市》位於拉差達,是近年興起的大型夜市。規劃整齊的攤位區與用餐區,比傳統夜市更有秩序但少了些野生感。美食攤位密度高,從日式串燒到泰北香腸都能找到,品質中上但缺乏特殊驚喜。年輕族群聚集,社群打卡氛圍濃厚。相較於恰圖恰或拉差達火車夜市的雜亂生猛,這裡更像是經過設計的夜市 2.0 版本——乾淨、安全、Instagram-friendly,但也因此失去了某種街頭的粗糙質感。適合初訪曼谷、想快速體驗夜市文化又不想面對混亂的旅人。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 934, "opening_hours": {"daily": "18:00-23:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 150}, {"id": "51beab30-da92-4acf-b8e3-aae8e6462ae3", "fax": null, "name": "芽莊四島遊", "tags": ["跳島", "浮潛", "派對船"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "nha-trang", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2026-04-04T11:24:20.979+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《芽莊四島遊》搭船前往芽莊灣周邊小島,浮潛、游泳、午餐、水上活動。船上有DJ播放音樂,氛圍歡樂。浮潛水質普通,魚群不多,但海水清澈。午餐在船上或島上餐廳,海鮮新鮮。這是芽莊標準行程——不深度,但輕鬆有趣,適合家庭、朋友。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Nha Trang Island Hopping", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "51c6432c-1b85-46b3-8506-516b8d969d33", "fax": null, "name": "芽莊四島跳島遊", "tags": ["跳島", "浮潛", "派對", "必玩"], "type": "a