.com/photos/268976/pexels-photo-268976.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940", "https://images.pexels.com/photos/7415261/pexels-photo-7415261.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940"], "address": null, "city_id": "ise", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 34.5083, "is_active": true, "longitude": 136.7833, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-01-23T02:46:31.369582+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "三重伊勢二見浦夫婦岩，兩塊巨岩矗立海中，繩索連接，象徵夫婦圓滿。大岩高9公尺、小岩高4公尺，繩索長35公尺，每年更換3次。日出時分，太陽從兩岩間升起，景色壯觀。這是日本結緣聖地，也是伊勢神宮參拜前的淨身之地。可搭配伊勢神宮、二見興玉神社一起參拜。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Meoto Iwa", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 100, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 45}, {"id": "5248280f-23da-4e6b-bb4c-8388f67e2c01", "fax": null, "name": "濟州民俗村", "tags": ["文化", "傳統", "茅草屋", "體驗", "歷史"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "重現濟州傳統村落的民俗村，保存100多間茅草屋。可了解濟州特有的文化和生活方式。有海女表演、傳統遊戲體驗。許多韓劇在此取景。\n\n旅遊提示：建議請導覽解說，更能了解濟州文化", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "jeju", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 33.3231, "is_active": true, "longitude": 126.8444, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:36.464879+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "濟州民俗村，展示濟州島傳統生活的戶外博物館。100多棟草屋、石牆、風車、傳統農具，重現19世紀濟州人生活場景。漁村、農村、山村三種生活型態都有展示。可以體驗傳統服飾、農事活動、民俗表演。這是認識濟州島歷史文化的最佳場所，也是親子教育的好去處。佔地廣闊，需預留2-3小時。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "Jeju Folk Village", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verif