動的體驗,遊客可餵食、幫大象洗澡、觀看大象踢足球、畫畫等才藝表演。園區強調動物福利,象群活動空間充足、照顧良好。騎象體驗路線穿越森林、溪流,感受泰國傳統交通方式。適合親子家庭、動物愛好者,是了解大象文化的好機會。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Elephant Village", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": "08:00-17:00", "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "53267211-106f-4d13-a9d4-1734a18f3d0b", "fax": null, "name": "神山登頂", "tags": ["登山", "挑戰", "日出", "神山", "探險"], "type": "experience", "notes": "挑戰東南亞最高峰，需要兩天一夜的行程。沿途可見不同海拔的植被變化，山頂可欣賞壯麗日出。需要提前預約。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "sabah", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 6.0757, "is_active": true, "longitude": 116.5587, "region_id": null, "country_id": "malaysia", "created_at": "2025-12-06T02:06:49.7041+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "神山登頂，東南亞最高峰攀登，海拔4,095公尺。第一天爬6公里到LabanRata山屋，第二天凌晨2點出發攻頂看日出。LowsPeak是最高點，360度俯瞰婆羅洲。這是登山愛好者夢想，也是沙巴最大挑戰。需許可、導遊、山屋預訂，約1,000-1,500馬幣/人。建議提前數月預訂。需體力與高山適應。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "MY", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 535, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 1440}, {"id": "53274d42-7b91-4efb-8f31-7d34aaaae1ba", "fax": null, "name": "馬尼拉大教堂", "tags": ["教堂", "地標", "歷史", "馬尼拉", "建築"], "type": "heritage", "notes": "馬尼拉的天主教主教座堂，經歷多次重建。現在的建築是二戰後重建的新羅馬式風格。內有玫瑰花窗和精美管風琴。\n\n旅遊提示：可免費參觀，但須注意服裝", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "manila", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 14.5995, "is_active": true, "longitude": 120.9842, "region_id": null, "country_id": "philippines", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:07:07.920453+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "馬尼拉大教堂，馬尼拉王城區最重要的天主教堂，建於1581年。羅馬式建築、彩繪玻璃窗、管風琴。這是馬尼拉必訪景點，也是認識菲律賓天主教文化的好地方。免費參觀，建議預留1小時。可搭配聖奧古斯丁教堂、聖地牙哥堡一起遊覽。需尊重禮拜。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "PH", "english_name": "Manila Cathedral", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 556, "opening_hours": {"daily": "06:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 30}, {"id": "53364791-e545-4fab-b234-f8a8823c803b", "fax": null, "name": "西斯廷教堂", "tags": ["教堂", "米開朗基羅", "創世紀", "最後審判", "梵蒂岡"], "type": "heritage", "notes": "米開朗基羅的曠世傑作，天花板的《創世紀》和祭壇的《最後審判》。是選舉教宗的地方。位於梵蒂岡博物館最後，禁止拍照和說話。\n\n旅遊提示：內部不能拍照和講話，要保持安靜", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 41.9029, "is_active": true, "longitude": 12.4545, "region_id": null, "country_id": "italy", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:06:36.859938+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "西斯廷教堂，義大利羅馬古蹟，展現古羅馬文明與文藝復興藝術。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "IT", "english_name": "Sistine Chapel", "ticket_price": "依官網而定", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 285, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 45}, {"id": "53370086-e671-41f3-a68d-2d8317cdd43a", "fax": null, "name": "下北澤", "tags": null, "type": "shopping", "notes": "古著與獨立音樂的聖地，二手唱片行與小劇場文青味濃厚。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://images.pexels.com/photos/531321/pexels-photo-531321.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940", "https://images.pexels.com/photos/281260/pexels-photo-281260.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940", "htt