", "notes": "東京市中心的神聖綠洲，走過神宮橋、穿越 10 萬棵樹木形成的參道，感受都會中的寧靜。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://wzvwmawpkapcmkfmkvav.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/resources/attractions/5b53747c-f2b7-4377-89af-aefbc0443952/1775722139680_89l8ngyme1k.webp"], "address": "", "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 35.6764, "is_active": true, "longitude": 139.6993, "region_id": "jp_kanto", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-06T06:44:03.033608+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "東京明治神宮，供奉明治天皇和昭憲皇太后。70萬平方公尺的森林，是東京都心綠洲。鳥居高12公尺，木製鳥居全日本最大。新年初詣參拜人數日本第一，達300萬人。本殿莊嚴肅穆，清酒桶、葡萄酒桶展示東西交流。這是東京最重要的神社，也是體驗日本傳統婚禮的地方。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Meiji Jingu Gaien Ginkgo", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 347, "opening_hours": {"daily": "日出至日落，約05:00-18:00（依季節調整）"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "5b57619d-dca6-47f1-a569-d7add6795454", "fax": null, "name": "金光石街", "tags": ["壁畫", "音樂", "懷舊", "街頭藝術", "散步"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "為紀念韓國民謠歌手金光石而建的壁畫街。牆上繪有他的畫像和歌詞。街道瀰漫懷舊氛圍，是文青最愛的散步路線。夜晚亮燈後更有情調。\n\n旅遊提示：建議傍晚來，拍照光線和氛圍都最佳", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "daegu", "website": null, "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": 35.8667, "is_active": true, "longitude": 128.6, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:01:17.352879+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "金光石街，韓國知名景點，值得一訪。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "Kim Kwang-seok Street", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 395, "opening_hours": {