9.7967, "region_id": "jp_kanto", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:49:05.568404+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《淺草人力車體驗》身著傳統服飾的車夫拉著雙人力車穿梭淺草巷弄，流利中英日文導覽淺草寺、仲見世通、隅田川沿岸秘境。車夫兼攝影師捕捉旅人與晴空塔同框美照，路線客製，解說歷史典故與在地美食。傳統與現代碰撞的移動風景。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Asakusa Rickshaw", "ticket_price": "¥5,000-20,000（依時間與人數）", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00（雨天停駛）"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "673009e0-cef5-46a7-b145-1fc61df1bfa3", "fax": null, "name": "上海小籠包", "tags": null, "type": "food", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 31.2312707, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.4700152, "region_id": "cn_east", "country_id": "china", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:55:56.150293+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "上海小籠包，最具代表性的上海美食。南翔饅頭店、鼎泰豐、佳家湯包都是名店。皮薄餡大、湯汁飽滿，咬開時湯汁噴濺，燙口但美味。吃法講究：夾起、咬破、吸汁、沾醋、入口。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "CN", "english_name": "Shanghai Xiaolongbao", "ticket_price": "約20-40元/籠", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 30, "opening_hours": {"daily": "依店家而異，通常07:00-21:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 30}, {"id": "674c2f2b-2ba5-4ee8-b697-172058be4a67", "fax": null, "name": "長安生態保護區", "tags": ["UNESCO世界遺產", "遊船", "喀斯特地貌", "電影取景", "一日遊"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "需時約3小時，建議穿著舒適、防曬。船上無法更換位置，建議早到選好位置。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 20.25, "is_active": true, "longitude": 105.9167, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2026-03-17T08:15:51.600585+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "寧平長安，UNESCO世界文化與自然雙遺產，越南版「陸上下龍灣」。搭乘手搖小船穿越石灰岩峰林，經過9個洞穴、翠綠稻田、古寺廟。船夫撐篙緩行，兩岸山峰倒映水面，寧靜如畫。電影《金剛：骷髏島》取景地。這是越南最美的喀斯特地貌景觀，也是河內周邊一日遊首選。遊船約3小時，建議早上前往，避開人潮。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "門票250,000越南盾（含遊船）", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"notes": "遊船最後出發時間約15:00，建議提前購票", "regular": {"open": "07:00", "close": "17:00"}}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "674cea45-200b-4b0e-ad2a-84e4910393dd", "fax": null, "name": "車埕車站", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "南投縣水里鄉車埕村民權巷2號", "city_id": "nantou-698c1821-d3e7-4008-a70e-7633ba447409", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 23.8336, "is_active": true, "longitude": 120.8653, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-01-09T03:43:44.063392+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "南投車埕的老火車站，是集集線的終點站。木造車站、老鐵道、木業展示館，保留了林業小鎮的歷史氛圍。車埕老街不長，卻有濃濃的懷舊感。這裡曾因木材產業繁榮，如今轉型為觀光景點，寧靜而美好。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": "Checheng Station", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 83, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放，木業展示館09:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "675db928-42d8-4d79-86e8-0ec77085b1e5", "fax": null, "name": "阿里山森林遊樂區", "tags": ["森林", "日出", "雲海", "鐵路"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "建議安排4-5小時，包含祝山線小火車、巨木群步道等", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "嘉義縣阿里山鄉", "city_id": null, "website": "https://www.ali-nsa.net/", "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 23.51, "is_active": true, "longitude": 120.805, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-03-17T03:13:22.597861+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "台灣最著名的森林遊樂區，以日出、雲海、晚霞、森林、鐵路五奇聞名。巨木群步道上的紅檜千年不朽，祝山線小火車穿梭在雲霧間，清晨的日出將阿里山染成金黃。這裡是認識台灣高山森林生態與林業文化的最佳場域。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": "Alishan National Forest Recreation Area", "ticket_price": "全票200元（平日150元），半票100元（平日80元）", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "24小時開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 240}, {"id": "6760d05e-5819-475d-866f-51026374dbc3", "fax": null, "name": "越南婦女博物館", "tags": ["女性博物館", "性別", "社會歷史"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "hanoi", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 21.0233507, "is_active": true, "longitude": 105.8515958, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2026-04-04T11:17:38.432+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《越南婦女博物館》展示越南女性在歷史、文化、社會中的角色。從古代女將軍、抗法抗美女戰士、到當代女性企業家,完整呈現女性如何參與國家建設。展覽包含傳統服飾、婚嫁習俗、生育文化、戰爭記憶。這不是歌功頌德的宣傳館,而是認真的性別研究展示——承認女性的貢獻,也不迴避她們面對的困境。英文說明詳盡,互動展區設計用心。這是河內少數主題明確、策展專業的博物館,值得花兩小時細看。理解一個國家,從理解女性的處境開始。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Vietnam Women's Museum", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": n