c-9f09-c394910b90de", "fax": null, "name": "機張蟹市場", "tags": ["螃蟹", "海鮮", "市場", "代客料理", "必吃"], "type": "market", "notes": "以雪蟹（紅蟹）聞名的海鮮市場，新鮮現撈。一樓市場選購，可請店家代為料理。價格比市區便宜許多。除了螃蟹也有各種海鮮。\n\n旅遊提示：建議2-3人吃一隻大蟹最划算", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "busan", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 35.1799528, "is_active": true, "longitude": 129.0752365, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:01:12.498988+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "釜山機張蟹市場，韓國最大的帝王蟹市場。帝王蟹、雪蟹、龍蝦、鮑魚應有盡有。可外帶或現場代煮。帝王蟹一隻約5-10萬韓元。這是釜山必訪景點，也是品嚐海鮮的好地方。免費參觀，建議預留2-3小時。可搭配海東龍宮寺、竹城聖堂一起遊覽。記得殺價。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "Gijang Crab Market", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 791, "opening_hours": {"daily": "約09:00-22:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "67dc83c3-6485-4f86-972c-bdad3a9b999d", "fax": null, "name": "淺草寺", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/67dc83c3-6485-4f86-972c-bdad3a9b999d-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/67dc83c3-6485-4f86-972c-bdad3a9b999d-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 35.7148, "is_active": true, "longitude": 139.7967, "region_id": "jp_kanto", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-01-23T00:38:30.671089+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "東京淺草寺，東京最古老的寺廟，建於628年。雷門大燈籠高3.9公尺，是淺草地標。仲見世通商店街販售人形燒、仙貝、和服小物。本堂供奉觀音菩薩，香火鼎盛。五重塔、淺草神社就在旁邊。穿和服在淺草散步，是東京最經典的體驗。這裡保留江戶下町風情，也是