 & Culture", "latitude": -7.9778384, "is_active": true, "longitude": 110.3672257, "region_id": null, "country_id": "indonesia", "created_at": "2025-12-06T02:07:00.408126+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "爪哇皮影戲，印尼傳統皮影戲，UNESCO非物質文化遺產。操偶師用皮革手工刻製人偶，搭配加美蘭音樂，演出Ramayana、Mahabharata等印度教史詩。在日惹或雅加達看正統版本最佳。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "ID", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 203, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "680838cb-f0c2-4d93-a622-3085a6b51296", "fax": null, "name": "孕婦湖", "tags": ["湖泊", "傳說", "自然", "蘭卡威", "遊船"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "蘭卡威的傳說湖泊，據說湖水有助受孕。四周群山環繞，湖水清澈。可乘船遊覽周邊的紅樹林。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "langkawi", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 6.35, "is_active": true, "longitude": 99.7833, "region_id": null, "country_id": "malaysia", "created_at": "2025-12-06T02:06:46.538086+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "蘭卡威孕婦湖，蘭卡威第二大島上的淡水湖，從空中看像懷孕婦女側躺，故名孕婦湖。傳說不孕婦女在此游泳後會懷孕。湖水清澈，可游泳、划獨木舟。這是蘭卡威跳島遊必訪景點，也是傳說故事所在地。跳島遊一日約200-300馬幣。可搭配紅樹林、老鷹餵食秀一起遊覽。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "MY", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 171, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "68139af4-c31a-4512-9278-40e87604df80", "fax": null, "name": "探秘藍眼淚", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://wzvwmawpkapcmkfmkvav.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/publ