": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": -8.515, "is_active": true, "longitude": 116.0917, "region_id": null, "country_id": "indonesia", "created_at": "2025-12-06T02:07:01.818957+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "薩薩克村，龍目島原住民薩薩克族的傳統村落。竹編屋、泥牆、茅草屋頂，保留傳統建築風格。村民示範傳統織布、編織、打鐵。尊重當地文化，拍照前請先詢問。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "ID", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 834, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "6eef7e34-eecc-46f4-8cb6-c26e9bd5c8bf", "fax": null, "name": "京都御所", "tags": null, "type": "heritage", "notes": "日本天皇居住千年的皇宮，現免費開放參觀。紫宸殿和御池庭展現皇室建築之美，需事前預約或當日排隊。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://images.pexels.com/photos/2887621/pexels-photo-2887621.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940", "https://images.pexels.com/photos/2389171/pexels-photo-2389171.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940", "https://images.pexels.com/photos/672820/pexels-photo-672820.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940", "https://images.pexels.com/photos/30324329/pexels-photo-30324329.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940", "https://images.pexels.com/photos/796216/pexels-photo-796216.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940"], "address": null, "city_id": "kyoto", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 35.0254, "is_active": true, "longitude": 135.7621, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:26.526958+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "日本皇室在京都的居所，自1331年至1869年遷都東京為止，是歷代天皇住所。紫宸殿、清涼殿等宮殿建築展現平安時代貴族文化。御苑四季景致優美，春櫻秋楓吸引遊客。自2016年起免費開放參觀，無需預約。周邊有京都御苑、下鴨神社、京都府立植物園。是了解日本皇室歷史與傳統建築的重要景點。", "contact_