ull, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "馬六甲三寶洞，馬六甲最大的中國佛教寺廟，建於1795年。供奉鄭和，紀念鄭和下西洋停靠馬六甲。寺廟建築融合中式與馬來風格，香火鼎盛。這是馬六甲重要文化遺產，也是認識鄭和歷史的好地方。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "MY", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 27, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "6f13f449-1d30-44e8-b9a4-764b31dfd015", "fax": null, "name": "Jeh O Chula 深夜酸辣東炎", "tags": ["網紅", "東炎", "宵夜", "排隊名店"], "type": "food", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/6f13f449-1d30-44e8-b9a4-764b31dfd015-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/6f13f449-1d30-44e8-b9a4-764b31dfd015-2.jpg"], "address": null, "city_id": "bangkok", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 13.7524938, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.4935089, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T06:44:06.976019+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "朱拉深夜東炎麵，曼谷24小時營業的深夜食堂，以酸辣蝦湯東炎麵聞名。湯頭濃郁酸辣、蝦新鮮、粉條Q彈。深夜2-4點最熱鬧，學生、上班族、夜貓子都來。這是曼谷必吃深夜美食，也是宵夜首選。一碗約80-120泰銖。位於朱拉隆功大學附近。全年無休，深夜最有氛圍。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Jeh O Chula", "ticket_price": "依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 933, "opening_hours": {"daily": "11:00-22:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "6f469e21-b311-44b7-a193-c951e6ee5c07", "fax": null, "name": "36行街", "tags": ["老街", "購物", "美食", "文化"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "imag