3607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《耶穌聖心堂》俗稱粉紅教堂,建於1870年代,整座建築從外牆到內部裝飾都是粉紅色。法式哥德建築與少女心配色形成奇妙對比,成為IG打卡熱點。教堂仍在使用,週日彌撒時禁止拍照。建議平日清晨前往,陽光將粉紅牆面染成更柔和的色調,遊客也較少。這座教堂提醒我們:宗教建築不一定要莊嚴肅穆,粉紅色也能表達虔誠。但請記得,這是宗教空間,不只是拍照景點。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Tan Dinh Pink Church", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "71c8e320-e8ca-4b6c-8385-ef0a6213c0c2", "fax": null, "name": "高野山", "tags": ["世界遺產", "宿坊", "空海"], "type": "temple", "notes": "空海大師開創的真言宗聖地，奧之院參道兩側 20 萬座墓碑震撼。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/71c8e320-e8ca-4b6c-8385-ef0a6213c0c2-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/71c8e320-e8ca-4b6c-8385-ef0a6213c0c2-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "wakayama", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 34.2167, "is_active": true, "longitude": 135.5833, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-06T06:57:33.261387+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "和歌山高野山，和歌山山上的宗教聖地，真言宗總本山金剛峯寺。奧之院、壇上伽藍、宿坊、精進料理、墓地參道。共通券1,宿坊體驗一泊二食約10,000-20,", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Mount Koya", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 566, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 300}, {"id": "71ea59bb-fc31-4e50-aac4-5b339218caba", "fax": null, "name": "極樂寺", "tags": ["佛寺", "觀音像", "纜車", "地標", "檳城"], "type": "temple", "notes": "東南亞最大的佛教寺廟之一，有七層寶塔和巨大觀音像。可搭纜車上山。融合中國、泰國、緬甸建築風格。新年期間有燈會。\n\n旅遊提示：搭纜車上去看觀音像視野最