分區、數十條巷弄間穿梭尋寶——從泰北手織棉布到復古搪瓷器皿，從多肉植物到定製皮件，幾乎所有你能想像的生活物件都能在這裡找到。正午時分氣溫飆升至40度，鐵皮屋頂下的空氣凝滯如糖漿，但討價還價聲依然此起彼落。資深買家懂得早上八點抵達，避開人潮搶購批發價的古著球鞋；在地人則直奔椰子冰與泰式奶茶攤，那是支撐他們走完整座市集的能量來源。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Chatuchak Weekend Market", "ticket_price": "免費入場", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"note": "平日部分區域營業", "weekend": "週六日09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 240}, {"id": "76975ecf-94d4-402a-ac61-d4b54e2dbf54", "fax": null, "name": "白象居", "tags": ["8D城市", "電影取景", "魔幻建築", "打卡"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "是居民樓，請輕聲參觀", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "重慶市渝中區白象街", "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "地標建築 / Landmark", "latitude": 29.56, "is_active": true, "longitude": 106.5783, "region_id": "cn_southwest", "country_id": "china", "created_at": "2025-12-05T14:34:25.630458+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "重慶「8D魔幻」的代表建築！24層樓高的老舊居民樓，沒有電梯但有三個出口分別在1樓、10樓、15樓，每個出口都連接不同的馬路。《少年的你》電影取景地，是體驗重慶立體城市的絕佳地點。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "CN", "english_name": "Baixiangju Building", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 14, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:30-17:30"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "76b8b8c0-a938-4823-8cc2-837a3bedbcaa", "fax": null, "name": "東茶屋街", "tags": ["老街", "金澤", "藝妓"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "保存完好的江戶時期茶屋街。可喝抹茶、買金箔冰淇淋。傍晚氣氛最好。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/76b8b8c0-a938-4823-8cc2-837a3bedbcaa-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/76b8b8c0-a938-4823-8cc2-837a3bedbcaa-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "kanazawa", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 36.57, "is_active": true, "longitude": 136.6736, "region_id": "jp_chubu", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-05T04:45:03.841359+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "金澤東茶屋街，金澤三大茶屋街之一，江戶時代花街保存完整。木造茶屋建築、金箔冰淇淋、九谷燒、加賀友禪、藝伎表演。這是金澤必訪景點，也是拍照打卡聖地。免費參觀，建議預留2-3小時。可搭配兼六園、金澤城一起遊覽。志摩茶屋可參觀內部。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Higashi Chaya District", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "76b8c04a-dae4-499e-af99-2e33a2ab6cd9", "fax": null, "name": "河內陶瓷馬賽克壁畫", "tags": ["壁畫", "公共藝術", "單車"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "hanoi", "website": null, "category": "地標建築 / Landmark", "latitude": 21.0478611, "is_active": true, "longitude": 105.8429179, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2026-04-04T11:17:37.799+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《河內陶瓷馬賽克壁畫》沿著紅河堤防延伸近4公里,是世界最長的陶瓷壁畫。2010年為慶祝河內建城千年而建,由越南與各國藝術家共同創作。壁畫內容涵蓋越南歷史、民間傳說、當代生活,色彩鮮豔風格多元。騎單車或機車沿著壁畫前行,是另類的河內體驗。這不是傳統觀光景點,而是城市藝術計畫的成果——公共空間、藝術創作與市民生活在此交會。壁畫沿線有咖啡館與小吃攤,適合花半天慢慢探索。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Hanoi Ceramic Mosaic Mural", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "76bafcb5-06fa-4cb5-8943-ff62a9f0544d", "fax": null, "name": "代官山", "tags": ["時尚", "咖啡", "