-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "停泊島環灘島，停泊島小島，背包客與潛水客天堂。LongBeach白沙灘最熱鬧，CoralBay適合浮潛。住宿便宜、氣氛輕鬆、海龜常出沒。這是馬來西亞必訪海島，也是東南亞潛水勝地之一。從瓜拉勿述搭船約45分鐘。可搭配大停泊島一起跳島。6-9月東北季風期關閉。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "MY", "english_name": "Mengalum Island", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 100, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 480}, {"id": "78d5d6bb-cda1-44e6-a6fe-5c180ac4e3a1", "fax": null, "name": "戰爭紀念館", "tags": null, "type": "museum", "notes": "韓戰歷史博物館，戶外展示各式戰機坦克，是軍事迷天堂。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "seoul", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 37.5361, "is_active": true, "longitude": 126.9775, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:33.68487+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "首爾戰爭紀念館，展示韓國軍事歷史，從古代到韓戰。戶外有坦克、戰機、軍艦展示。6.25韓戰館最震撼，展示南北分裂、戰爭與和平。這是認識韓國現代史的好地方，也是首爾必訪景點。免費參觀，建議預留3-4小時。可搭配梨泰院、龍山一起遊覽。周一休館。戶外展覽免費拍照。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "War Memorial of Korea", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-20:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 150}, {"id": "78fb92a5-0f28-47fd-9fe7-ed614c0aecc1", "fax": null, "name": "隅田川水上巴士", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://wzvwmawpkapcmkfmkvav.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/resources/attractions/78fb92a5-0f28-47fd-9fe7-ed614c0aecc1/1775722174029_0y56ab8huj8f.jpg"], "address": "", "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-04-09T08:02:05.915351+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "隅田川水上巴士是連結淺草與台場、濱離宮等景點的經典水上交通方式，能從河面欣賞東京晴空塔、彩虹大橋及隅田川上的多座特色橋樑。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "7955b63f-50d7-44a8-96f7-3d9485500111", "fax": null, "name": "大象自然公園", "tags": ["大象保育", "倫理旅遊", "動物救援"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "道德大象保護區，可餵食、幫大象洗澡，但不騎象。半日或全日遊約2500-5000泰銖。需預約。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/7955b63f-50d7-44a8-96f7-3d9485500111-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/7955b63f-50d7-44a8-96f7-3d9485500111-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 19.214683, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.8616387, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:39.423666+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《大象自然公園》Elephant Nature Park 是清邁最知名的大象保育機構,創辦人 Lek Chailert 從馬戲團、伐木業、觀光業救出退役大象,提供終身安養。園區禁止騎象、看表演,只能餵食、洗澡、觀察。你會聽到每頭大象的故事——背上的傷疤來自鐵鉤、眼睛失明因為虐待、個性溫柔是因為年老。站在河裡幫五噸重的大象刷洗,水花濺起時你會感受到生命的重量與溫度。這不是娛樂,而是關於如何與其他物種共存的倫理課程。門票收入全數用於大象照護,這是負責任旅遊的實踐。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Elephant Nature Park", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_u