6-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "小琉球觀音石,狀似觀音菩薩盤坐的天然珊瑚礁岩,是小琉球著名的奇岩景觀。從特定角度觀看,岩石輪廓確實神似觀音坐姿,頭部、身軀、坐姿都栩栩如生。大自然的巧合與海浪千年雕琢,讓這塊礁岩成為島上的祈福地標。許多遊客來此祈願,也是攝影愛好者捕捉奇岩的熱門景點。退潮時可以更靠近觀察,但需注意安全。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": "Guanyin Rock", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 15}, {"id": "7b600b84-444f-4656-91fe-88d4fa0d18e0", "fax": null, "name": "金鞭溪", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 29.3338673, "is_active": true, "longitude": 110.4389038, "region_id": null, "country_id": "china", "created_at": "2025-12-06T02:12:20.299383+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "金鞭溪，中國知名景點，值得探訪。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "CN", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 400, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:30-17:30"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "7b615f05-1f13-4a66-b64c-35fb65a18e80", "fax": null, "name": "華閭古都", "tags": ["古都遺址", "歷史", "寺廟", "文化遺產"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "建議請導遊講解歷史背景，更能理解遺址意義。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 20.2556, "is_active": true, "longitude": 105.9167, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2026-03-17T08:15:51.600585+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "寧平華閭，10-11世紀越南丁朝與前黎朝的首都遺址。保留丁先皇廟、黎大行廟兩座寺廟，展示越南古代建築風格。石碑、石龍、宮殿遺跡述說著千年歷史。這是認識越南古代歷史的重要景點，也是寧平文化遺產。門票20,000越南盾，適合歷史愛好者。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "門票20,000越南盾", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"regular": {"open": "07:00", "close": "17:00"}}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "7b8e096c-72ea-497f-8010-d40ab4e9f991", "fax": null, "name": "Mahanakhon Skywalk", "tags": ["地標", "天空步道", "夜景", "高空"], "type": "viewpoint", "notes": "曼谷最高建築的玻璃天空步道，78層樓高。透明地板讓人俯瞰城市，刺激又震撼。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/7b8e096c-72ea-497f-8010-d40ab4e9f991-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/7b8e096c-72ea-497f-8010-d40ab4e9f991-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "bangkok", "website": null, "category": "地標建築 / Landmark", "latitude": 13.7244, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.5292, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:38.317334+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《Mahanakhon Skywalk》位於King Power Mahanakhon大樓78樓,是曼谷最高的360度透明天空步道。腳下玻璃地板可直視314公尺高空下的車流人潮,腎上腺素瞬間飆升。建議傍晚前往,先欣賞日落將曼谷天際線染成金紅,再看夜幕降臨,萬家燈火逐一亮起,昭披耶河如銀帶蜿蜒。頂樓Rooftop Bar供應調酒,可在高空中小酌,俯瞰這座永不入睡的城市。門票含Sky Tray餐飲折抵,適合安排2-3小時體驗。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Mahanakhon Skywalk", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "7bb9f361-330b-4d72-9944-d9f74d4e1a58", "fax": null, "name": "岡山縣立美術館", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "no