"deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "越南漆畫是融合法國美術與越南傳統漆藝的獨特藝術形式，在20世紀初由河內美術學院創立，並在順化皇宮得到發展。在順化（峴港附近）的漆藝工作室，跟隨越南國家級漆畫藝術家學習傳統漆畫技法。使用天然漆液、蛋殼、金箔、螺鈿，創作一幅越南風景或花鳥漆畫。學習磨顯技法：多層上漆、打磨，呈現漆畫特有的光澤與層次。漆畫需要耐心與時間，完整作品需數週完成，工坊提供郵寄服務。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Hue Royal Lacquer Painting Workshop", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 0}, {"id": "7d289cb6-4f23-437d-a346-df9c84d44388", "fax": null, "name": "西本願寺", "tags": null, "type": "temple", "notes": "淨土真宗本願寺派總本山，世界遺產，阿彌陀堂氣勢恢宏。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/7d289cb6-4f23-437d-a346-df9c84d44388-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/7d289cb6-4f23-437d-a346-df9c84d44388-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "kyoto", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 34.9914, "is_active": true, "longitude": 135.7514, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:27.09701+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "西本願寺，日本佛教寺院，展現日本傳統寺廟建築與庭園造景之美。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Nishi Honganji", "ticket_price": "免費或300-500日圓", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "06:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "7d3f5744-92ff-4f41-b5a6-2b4fec7bb519", "fax": null, "name": "故宮博物院", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "台北市士林區至善路二段221號", "c