l, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《帕邢寺》與帕辛寺為同一寺廟的不同譯名,Wat Phra Singh 在清邁古城西側,是蘭納王朝皇室寺廟。寺內的Lai Kham佛殿是蘭納建築的精品,金色屋簷在陽光下反射刺眼光芒,木雕窗櫺細膩到讓人屏息。殿內供奉的Phra Singh佛像據說來自斯里蘭卡,是清邁最受尊敬的佛像之一。每天傍晚時分,在地信眾會來此參拜,點燭、獻花、靜坐,虔誠氛圍濃厚。寺廟腹地寬廣,有多座佛塔與佛殿,值得花一小時慢慢探索。這裡遊客雖多,但仍保有宗教空間該有的肅穆感。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Wat Phra Singh", "ticket_price": "成人100-200泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "8027f028-4f6a-44e6-826f-38af7a5b1712", "fax": null, "name": "安縵吉沃", "tags": ["奢華", "酒店", "安縵", "日惹", "婆羅浮屠"], "type": "hotel", "notes": "安縵集團在日惹的頂級度假村，可遠眺婆羅浮屠。獨棟Villa設計，極致私密。可安排私人婆羅浮屠日出體驗。是世界頂級酒店之一。\n\n旅遊提示：預算充足的話，婆羅浮屠日出私人體驗非常特別", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "bali", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": -8.2271303, "is_active": true, "longitude": 115.1919203, "region_id": null, "country_id": "indonesia", "created_at": "2025-12-06T02:12:35.04923+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "安縵吉沃度假村，爪哇島最頂級的度假村，位於婆羅浮屠附近。36棟Suite與Villa環繞圓形泳池，如同佛塔佈局。無邊際視野面向婆羅浮屠與默拉皮火山。私人婆羅浮屠日出行程、爪哇傳統文化體驗。距婆羅浮屠約15分鐘車程。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "ID", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "約Rp 50,000-200,000", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 234, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "80330287-4877-4387-b1aa-e2b0b3eb31fe", "fax": null, "name": "處女島", "tags": ["沙洲", "潮汐", "浮潛", "海膽", "薄荷島"], "type": "beach", "notes": "薄荷島旁的沙洲，退潮時出現長長的白沙。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "bohol", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 9.5167, "is_active": true, "longitude": 124.05, "region_id": null, "country_id": "philippines", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:26:59.982113+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "薄荷島處女島，薄荷島外海的白沙洲，退潮時露出長條形沙灘，漲潮時被海水淹沒。可游泳、浮潛、買海鮮BBQ、拍照。這是薄荷島必訪景點，也是跳島遊熱門。包含在跳島遊行程。建議退潮時前往。可搭配巴里卡薩島一起遊覽。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "PH", "english_name": "Virgin Island", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "804b91c8-4470-497b-9139-6ee753d5de88", "fax": null, "name": "僧侶布施體驗", "tags": ["托鉢", "佛教", "清晨儀式"], "type": "experience", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/804b91c8-4470-497b-9139-6ee753d5de88-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/804b91c8-4470-497b-9139-6ee753d5de88-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 18.7882778, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.9858802, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:49:11.531886+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《僧侶布施體驗》Monk Almsgiving 是泰國佛教的日常儀式,清晨時分僧侶赤足托鉢接受信眾布施。清邁古城內,每天清晨五點半到六點半,僧侶會沿固定路線行走。信眾跪坐路旁,將糯米飯、水果、零食放入僧侶的缽中。這不是表演,而是真實的宗教實踐——僧侶不能自己採買食物,必須仰賴布施維生。若想參與,請先了解禮儀:女性不可觸碰僧侶、食物需事先準備、跪姿表示尊敬。許多旅店提供布施食物包,但也可以前往市場自己採買。這是用身體理解佛教文化的方式——清晨、安靜、虔誠。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Monk Almsgiving", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": fals