"display_order": 70, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:30-17:30"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 30}, {"id": "81adb3ee-ac22-470e-9851-bbed5ba83e7a", "fax": null, "name": "芽莊市場", "tags": ["傳統市場", "生鮮", "在地"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "nha-trang", "website": null, "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": 12.2549685, "is_active": true, "longitude": 109.1917922, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2026-04-04T11:24:21.614+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《芽莊市場》Dam Market是芽莊最大的傳統市場,生鮮、乾貨、服飾應有盡有。價格便宜,但需要議價。市場內有小吃攤,越南法式麵包、河粉都是銅板價。這裡不是觀光景點,而是在地人的日常。市場證明:即使是度假城市,傳統生活依然存在。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Dam Market", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "81b0f63e-e1df-429c-b5c5-837bde6db3c4", "fax": null, "name": "Terminal 21", "tags": ["購物中心", "主題", "美食街"], "type": "shopping", "notes": "曼谷阿索克的主題購物中心，每層樓代表不同城市。從加勒比到東京，設計獨特有趣。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/81b0f63e-e1df-429c-b5c5-837bde6db3c4-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/81b0f63e-e1df-429c-b5c5-837bde6db3c4-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "bangkok", "website": null, "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": 13.7378, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.56, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:37.546376+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《Terminal 21 購物中心》把機場航站樓概念搬進Asok捷運站旁。每層樓設定為一座城市主題：一樓是羅馬競技場石柱、三樓是東京澀谷街景、五樓是舊金山漁人碼頭，樓層指示牌模仿機場登機門編號，連洗手間都依城市風格打造——東京女廁是溫柔粉色系，倫敦男廁掛著紅色電話亭。這種略顯刻意的主題包裝在曼谷年輕人眼中卻恰到好處，他們在這裡消費的不只是服飾與餐飲，更是一種「不出國也能環遊世界」的平價想像。地下美食街永遠人滿為患,炸雞、壽司、義大利麵在同一個托盤上共存，是全球化最通俗也最真誠的樣貌。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Terminal 21", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "81c2075e-26e4-44a6-83d3-359cdbe7d1a0", "fax": null, "name": "書院門古文化街", "tags": ["文房四寶", "書法", "文藝", "古玩", "小眾"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "可與碑林博物館連遊", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "西安市碑林區書院門街", "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": 34.2567, "is_active": true, "longitude": 108.9467, "region_id": "cn_northwest", "country_id": "china", "created_at": "2025-12-05T14:34:26.42475+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "書院門古文化街，中國傳統商業街區或市場，販售各式商品美食與文創紀念品。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "CN", "english_name": "Shuyuanmen Ancient Culture Street", "ticket_price": "免費或5-20元", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 11, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放，商店約09:00-21:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "81dd37e8-53ee-47b5-8540-65c632feb0cf", "fax": null, "name": "河內夜間美食導覽", "tags": ["美食導覽", "街頭小吃", "在地體驗"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "hanoi", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 21.0339986, "is_active": true, "longitude": 105.8521332, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2026-04-04T11:17:38.196+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《河內夜間美食導覽》由在地導遊帶領,用三小時吃遍舊城區小吃。從河粉、春捲、法式麵包、烤肉串、蛋咖啡到甜品,每站都是在地人推薦的老店。導遊會解釋每道菜的歷史、作法、吃法,也會分享河內的生活故事。坐在街邊塑膠矮凳上,與越南家庭一起用餐,是最真實的文化體驗。這不是高級餐廳巡禮,而是街頭飲食文化的深度探索。選擇小團體(6-8人)的導覽,互動品質較好。河內的精華不在博物館,而在街頭——美食導覽是理解這座城市最快的方式。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Hanoi Street Food Tour", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "81dd6937-a10a-4968-a954-c5f34bfdefc1", "fax": null, "name": "胡志明市夜景遊船", "tags": ["遊船", "夜景", "自助餐"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "ho-chi-minh", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2026-04-04T11:19:46.647+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《胡志明市夜景遊船》沿西貢河航行,兩岸是現代建築與殖民時期別墅交錯的天際線。船上提供越南料理自助餐與傳統音樂表演,氛圍浪漫但略顯觀光化。重點不是餐點或表演,而是從水上看城市的角度——燈火輝煌的Landmark 81、復古的中央郵局、熱鬧的碼頭區,在河面上構成流動的畫面。適合情侶或家庭,不適合深度旅人。這是輕鬆的觀光體驗,不要期待太多,就不會失望。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Saigon River Dinner Cruise", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "81fdca9c-bbce-4287-a6e6-047d5ed7cbe5", "fax": null, "name": "仙本那卡帕萊島", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "sabah", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 4.5012, "is_active": true, "longitude": 118.6712, "region_id": null, "