uto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940"], "address": null, "city_id": "takayama", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 36.143133, "is_active": true, "longitude": 137.257691, "region_id": "jp_chubu", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:55:47.685389+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "岐阜高山五平餅，日本中部山區特色小吃。粳米搗成餅，串在竹籤上，塗上味噌、醬油、芝麻醬，炭火烤至香脆。口感外脆內軟，醬料香甜鹹香。高山老街、中山道、木曾路都能吃到。這是飛驒地區傳統美食，也是逛街必吃小吃。一串建議現烤現吃。可搭配飛驒牛、朴葉味噌一起品嚐。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Gohei Mochi", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "87075dfe-3b45-4b65-a110-4bafd908e161", "fax": null, "name": "文華東方吉隆坡", "tags": ["酒店", "奢華", "文華東方", "雙子塔", "吉隆坡"], "type": "hotel", "notes": "吉隆坡頂級酒店，緊鄰雙子塔。東方文華招牌的奢華服務和精緻餐飲，城市景觀房可欣賞雙子塔。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "kuala-lumpur", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 3.1954331, "is_active": true, "longitude": 101.6798541, "region_id": null, "country_id": "malaysia", "created_at": "2025-12-06T02:12:37.35495+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "文華東方吉隆坡，吉隆坡頂級酒店，位於雙峰塔旁。房間寬敞奢華、服務無可挑剔、無邊際泳池可看雙峰塔。LaiPoHeen粵菜餐廳是米其林推薦，Mosaic餐廳自助餐豐富。這是吉隆坡最頂級的酒店之一，也是商務與度假的完美選擇。房價每晚約1,500馬幣起。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "MY", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 123, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "871c4a48-a4ab-4e0a-ba03-1988779c6c7