"2025-12-06T01:27:02.398864+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "多爾瑪巴赫切宮，土耳其歷史文化景點，橫跨歐亞文明交匯處，融合拜占庭、鄂圖曼與現代文化。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TR", "english_name": "Dolmabahce Palace", "ticket_price": "成人500-750土耳其里拉", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"note": "週一休館", "open": "09:00", "close": "16:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "9c8dbf0d-e1b0-420e-8af3-e740a6477bc0", "fax": null, "name": "昭披耶河遊船", "tags": ["公共交通", "河岸風光", "在地體驗"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "曼谷湄南河的遊船體驗，是欣賞沿岸景點的方式。從大皇宮到鄭王廟，水上交通便利又有風情。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/9c8dbf0d-e1b0-420e-8af3-e740a6477bc0-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/9c8dbf0d-e1b0-420e-8af3-e740a6477bc0-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "bangkok", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 13.725, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.5108, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-10-28T08:53:14.026234+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《昭披耶河遊船》不同於觀光遊船的包裝行程,搭乘公共渡船是體驗昭披耶河最在地的方式。橘色旗幟的快船是通勤族的選擇,速度快,停靠站少,票價便宜。藍色旗幟的觀光船停靠所有主要景點,船上有英文廣播。站在船尾,河風迎面吹來,兩岸的寺廟、高樓、棚屋、飯店快速後退,構成曼谷階級差異的視覺拼貼。船家熟練地拋繩、靠岸、開船,動作流暢如儀式。這是水上城市的日常交通,沒有浪漫的濾鏡,只有實用主義的效率。但當夕陽將河面染成金色,你會瞬間理解為什麼人們說昭披耶河是曼谷的生命線。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Chao Phraya River Cruise", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 10, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null