 Shopping", "latitude": 13.7042168, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.5028259, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-11-01T10:48:49.677668+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《Asiatique河濱夜市》由百年碼頭倉庫改建,保留紅磚牆與木樑結構,融合復古與現代風情。1,500間商店與餐廳沿湄南河畔排列,60公尺高摩天輪是地標,夜晚彩燈璀璨,倒映在河面如夢似幻。可從Saphan Taksin BTS站搭免費接駁船直達,晚風徐徐,河景浪漫。購物選擇豐富,從泰絲、香薰、手工藝品到國際品牌應有盡有。人妖秀Calypso Cabaret也在此駐點演出,是曼谷結合購物、美食、娛樂的一站式夜生活聖地。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Asiatique The Riverfront", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "18:00-23:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "9e4576a4-d22f-4cce-a235-c650a19630e6", "fax": null, "name": "巴黎迪士尼", "tags": ["主題樂園", "迪士尼", "親子", "遊樂設施", "巴黎近郊"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "歐洲唯一的迪士尼樂園，有兩個園區。睡美人城堡是粉紅色的。有獨特的巴黎風情和歐洲限定活動。距巴黎約40分鐘RER。\n\n旅遊提示：買兩園票可以玩得比較完整", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "主題樂園 / Theme Park", "latitude": 48.8700934, "is_active": true, "longitude": 2.7740499, "region_id": "ile-de-france", "country_id": "france", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:04:22.034585+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "巴黎迪士尼，法國巴黎著名景點，展現藝術與文化之都魅力。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "FR", "english_name": "Disneyland Paris", "ticket_price": "依官網而定", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 120, "opening_hours": {"open": "09:30", "close": "23:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 600}, {"id": "9e7929c2-562f-4dce-a0c0-dcfb57152b33", "fax": null, "name": "巴拉庫達湖", "tags": null, "type"