15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《鳴澤冰穴》青木原樹海環狀熔岩洞，總長 153 公尺、深達 21 公尺，狹窄處需彎腰前行。內部冰柱終年不融、天然製冰池昔日儲藏冰塊至東京，洞頂熔岩鐘乳與冰壁共存奇景。溫差大、濕滑陡峭，穿著舒適鞋履與外套。與富岳風穴套票更划算。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Narusawa Ice Cave", "ticket_price": "¥350（成人），與富岳風穴套票 ¥600", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 100, "opening_hours": {"summer": "09:00-17:00（4-11月）", "winter": "09:00-16:00（12-3月）"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 45}, {"id": "a2c5164f-521a-40a6-8656-a207ba0ec1b2", "fax": null, "name": "永旺夢樂城沖繩來客夢", "tags": ["購物", "寶可夢", "親子", "美食"], "type": "shopping", "notes": "", "phone": "", "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/workspace-files/attractions/1766562571492_d1kzgb.png"], "address": "", "city_id": "naha", "website": "", "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": 26.3147, "is_active": true, "longitude": 127.7631, "region_id": "jp_okinawa", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-20T12:18:03.766249+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "位於沖繩中部，是規模最大的購物中心，擁有超過兩百個品牌進駐。館內最壯觀的莫過於入口處的巨型水族箱，能近距離欣賞熱帶魚悠游。無論是國際流行服飾、家電、生活用品或美食餐飲一應俱全。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "AEON MALL Okinawa Rycom", "ticket_price": "成人500-700日圓", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 181, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-17:00（依季節調整）"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": "https://maps.app.goo.gl/7oRpnGffC4DGW6is8", "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "a2e32d47-4140-40aa-857a-520ba39ebda1", "fax": null, "name": "崇聖寺三塔", "tags": null, "type": "heritage", "notes": "門票包含崇聖寺和三塔，建議上午前往光線較佳", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": "https://www.dali.gov.cn/", "category": "景點 / Attraction", "