null, "duration_minutes": 300}, {"id": "a5fb2f54-c73d-4a93-a7b6-ef18129e53bd", "fax": null, "name": "城山日出峰", "tags": ["世界遺產", "火山", "日出", "登山", "濟州代表"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "UNESCO世界自然遺產，登頂約需30分鐘，建議日出時分前往", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "jeju", "website": "https://www.jeju.go.kr/seongsan/index.htm", "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 33.4585, "is_active": true, "longitude": 126.9425, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2025-10-27T15:26:40.818404+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "濟州島城山日出峰，UNESCO世界自然遺產。10萬年前海底火山爆發形成的火山口，直徑600公尺，99塊尖石圍繞火山口。登頂約30分鐘，火山口景觀壯觀，可俯瞰濟州東部海岸。清晨看日出最美，太陽從海平面升起，將火山口染成金黃。這是濟州島必訪景點。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "Seongsan Ilchulbong", "ticket_price": "成人5000韓元", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 2, "opening_hours": {"daily": "日出前開放至20:00", "sunrise": "夏季約05:30，冬季約07:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "a61711ee-9c96-4dde-b7b3-b749c343c2dd", "fax": null, "name": "清邁古城", "tags": ["古城", "單車", "生活"], "type": "heritage", "notes": "護城河環繞的方形古城，有多座城門。可租單車或摩托車遊覽。古城內有眾多寺廟、咖啡廳。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/a61711ee-9c96-4dde-b7b3-b749c343c2dd-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/a61711ee-9c96-4dde-b7b3-b749c343c2dd-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 18.7883, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.9853, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T06:50:00.736637+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《清邁古城》是一片方正的歷史留白,護城河與殘存的紅磚城牆框出七百年前的邊界。城內巷弄依舊保持人的尺度,寺廟、咖啡館、民宿與老宅院交錯分布,沒有刻意規劃的觀光動線,只有自然生長的生活紋理。清晨時分,僧侶赤足托鉢穿過巷道,午後陽光將金色佛塔的影子投向石板路。這裡不是被圍欄保護的遺址,而是時間持續流動的場域——古城從未停止使用,因此也從未真正成為「古蹟」,而是活著的城市切片。租輛單車在古城內穿梭,是理解這座城市最好的方式。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Chiang Mai Old City", "ticket_price": "免費（部分寺廟收費20-40泰銖）", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 598, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天，寺廟約06:00-18:00", "sunday_market": "週日16:00-22:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 240}, {"id": "a63245b0-84af-45a2-92f8-c9799f2258da", "fax": null, "name": "Phi Phi 群島跳島", "tags": ["跳島", "浮潛", "皮皮島"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "通常包含大小皮皮島、蚊子島、竹子島。瑪雅灣每天有限流管制。建議住一晚更悠閒。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/a63245b0-84af-45a2-92f8-c9799f2258da-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/a63245b0-84af-45a2-92f8-c9799f2258da-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "krabi", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 7.7522403, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.7766434, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-11-01T12:55:07.273266+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "喀比 Phi Phi 群島跳島，從喀比或普吉出發的經典跳島行程。Phi Phi Don、Phi Phi Leh、Bamboo Island、Monkey Beach。浮潛、海灘、石灰岩峭壁，景色震撼。這是喀比必體驗活動，也是泰國最美海島之一。一日遊約 1,500-2,500 泰銖。建議 11-4 月前往。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Phi Phi Islands", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 480}, {"id": "a63eaea1-8445-4ede-