 "opening_hours": {"note": "每日限300人入內", "open": "08:00", "close": "17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "a8dff2a8-24a2-4532-a290-676bbb2508af", "fax": null, "name": "藏王纜車", "tags": ["纜車", "樹冰", "觀景", "滑雪"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://wzvwmawpkapcmkfmkvav.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/resources/attractions/a8dff2a8-24a2-4532-a290-676bbb2508af/1775617366059_040rcn7s0eaz.jpg"], "address": "", "city_id": "yamagata", "website": null, "category": "地標建築 / Landmark", "latitude": 38.1533452, "is_active": true, "longitude": 140.4219458, "region_id": "jp_tohoku", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-04-01T08:25:11.615132+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《藏王纜車》分為山麓線與山頂線，全程約17分鐘，將遊客送上海拔1661公尺的地藏山頂。冬季是賞樹冰（雪怪）的最佳方式,纜車緩緩爬升，窗外針葉林逐漸被厚雪覆蓋，形成超現實的冰雪雕塑群,壯觀震撼。春夏則可俯瞰綠意盎然的山谷與火山湖「御釜」的翡翠色澤。山頂設有展望台與餐廳,天氣晴朗時,月山、鳥海山、甚至太平洋海岸線都清晰可見,是東北地區最具代表性的空中纜車體驗。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Zao Ropeway", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "a8efaf0a-a966-44ba-bfff-6395e0b56e63", "fax": null, "name": "JAJA素食餐廳", "tags": ["網紅", "打卡", "素食"], "type": "food", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 22.2792968, "is_active": true, "longitude": 114.1628907, "region_id": null, "country_id": "china", "created_at": "2025-12-06T06:44:08.542404+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "JAJA素食餐廳，北京三里屯的創意素食餐廳。用蔬菜、豆製品、菌菇創作出精緻料理，顛覆對素食的刻板印象。松露蘑菇pizza、牛油果塔塔、素食漢堡都是招牌。餐廳設計