re", "latitude": 35.005, "is_active": true, "longitude": 135.7831, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:27.204318+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "知恩院，日本知名景點，值得造訪體驗。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Chion-in", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "b2f56a3b-7d64-4133-9f09-53a643bc5485", "fax": null, "name": "岡山後樂園", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": "日本三大名園之一，春季櫻花、秋季楓葉最美，建議預留1.5小時", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/b2f56a3b-7d64-4133-9f09-53a643bc5485-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/b2f56a3b-7d64-4133-9f09-53a643bc5485-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "okayama", "website": "https://okayama-korakuen.jp/", "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 34.6633, "is_active": true, "longitude": 133.9347, "region_id": "jp_chugoku", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-01-23T02:44:39.926573+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "岡山後樂園，日本三大名園之一，1700年建造。池泉回遊式庭園、唯心山、流店、延養亭、梅林、櫻花、芝生。旭川旁，可看岡山城背景。春季櫻花、秋季紅葉、夏季夜間點燈都很美。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Korakuen Garden", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 100, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "b301a2a1-a69c-4347-9700-1687563275a6", "fax": null, "name": "清邁禪修寺廟七日靜修", "tags": ["養生靜修", "頂級體驗"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "頂級體驗 | 養生靜修 | 價位: | 難度:None", "phone": null, "images": ["https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506905925346-21bda4d32df4?w=800", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552465011-b4e21bf6e79a?w=800"], "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2026-04-06T22:24:13.2978+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "在清邁山區的寧靜寺廟，進行七日內觀禪修（Vipassana）靜修。這是上座部佛教最核心的禪修方法，通過觀察呼吸與身體感受，達到內心的平靜與洞察。七天中保持聖默（Noble Silence），不說話、不眼神交流，專注於內在修行。每日清晨4:30起床，進行坐禪、行禪、聆聽佛法開示。享用兩餐簡單素食（過午不食）。由資深禪修導師每日一對一指導，調整姿勢與心態。這是深度的心靈排毒與自我覺察之旅，適合想暫時離開喧囂、尋找內在平靜的人。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Chiang Mai Vipassana Meditation 7 Days", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 0}, {"id": "b30e9b1a-56c5-406c-91cc-1e8a13597f41", "fax": null, "name": "會安古城", "tags": ["世界遺產", "古鎮", "會安"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "同會安古鎮。農曆14滿月時有燈籠節，全城點蠟燭，非常夢幻。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "hoi-an", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 15.8801, "is_active": true, "longitude": 108.338, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2025-11-01T13:04:52.129679+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "會安古城，UNESCO世界文化遺產。15-19世紀國際貿易港，保留完整的古建築、會館、寺廟、古宅。黃色牆面、木雕窗櫺、燈籠高掛，充滿古樸韻味。日本橋、福建會館、陳富街是精華。白天逛古蹟，夜晚燈籠點亮河面，如夢似幻。這是越南最美的古鎮，也是必訪景點。需購買古城通票，可參觀5個景點。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Hoi An Ancient Town", "ticket_