", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 33.6833, "is_active": true, "longitude": 135.35, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-01-23T02:46:27.715029+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "白濱溫泉，日本溫泉鄉，泉質優良，是放鬆身心的絕佳溫泉勝地。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Shirahama Onsen", "ticket_price": "約500-1500日圓/人", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 100, "opening_hours": {"daily": "依溫泉業者營業時間"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "b32bb80c-7b5e-4a0f-8407-ba54cda9ce05", "fax": null, "name": "科隆島", "tags": ["沉船潛水", "溫泉湖", "跳島", "清澈湖水", "巴拉望"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "巴拉望北部的跳島天堂，以二戰日本沉船潛水和凱央根湖聞名。湖水清澈見底被譽為菲律賓最乾淨的湖。有溫泉湖可泡。\n\n旅遊提示：凱央根湖需爬一小段山路才能到達", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 11.9988, "is_active": true, "longitude": 120.204, "region_id": null, "country_id": "philippines", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:07:07.066916+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "科隆島，巴拉望省北部的離島，以石灰岩峭壁、潟湖、沉船潛水、溫泉聞名。凱央根湖、雙子潟湖、巴拉庫達湖、沉船潛點都是必訪。跳島遊約1,500-2,從馬尼拉飛行約1小時。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "PH", "english_name": "Coron", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 466, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 480}, {"id": "b33fc74d-8536-4691-a452-338fdbfa736c", "fax": null, "name": "太魯閣國家公園", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": "需於入園前3-30天線上申請許可，每日有名額限制，砂卡礑、燕子口、白楊步道需申請", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "花蓮縣秀林鄉富世村富世291號", "city_id": "769364e9-d3e2-474f-bc80-0184c00e6d9e", "website": "https://www.taroko.gov.tw/", "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 23.8225, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.6044, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-01-09T03:36:28.944514+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "花蓮太魯閣國家公園，立霧溪切割大理石形成的峽谷，是台灣最壯觀的地質景觀。從太魯閣閣口進入，峽谷兩側峭壁高聳，最窄處僅20公尺寬。砂卡礑步道、燕子口、九曲洞，每條步道都展現不同的峽谷風貌。1914年日本開鑿合歡越嶺道，1956年開闢中橫公路，225位工程人員殉職，長春祠紀念他們的犧牲。這不只是風景區，更是台灣開發史的見證。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": "Taroko National Park", "ticket_price": "免費（部分步道需申請入園許可，如錐麓古道200元）", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 31, "opening_hours": {"note": "颱風或豪雨後部分步道封閉", "daily": "全天開放", "trails": "部分步道需線上申請，07:00-10:00入園", "visitor_center": "08:30-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 300}, {"id": "b34bd150-c03a-47a8-a412-1da01108c4cb", "fax": null, "name": "獅身人面像", "tags": ["世界遺產", "古蹟", "地標", "攝影"], "type": "heritage", "notes": "與金字塔同一園區，建議一起參觀。最佳拍照位置在正面稍遠處。聲光秀每晚舉行，需另外購票。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 29.9752811, "is_active": true, "longitude": 31.1375124, "region_id": "eg_cairo", "country_id": "egypt", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:27:05.635985+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "獅身人面像，埃及古文明遺跡，見證法老王朝數千年歷史，展現古埃及建築藝術與文化成就。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "EG", "english_name": "Sphinx", "ticket_price": "依官網而定", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"open": "08:00", "close": "17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "b354e0f5-883d-4860-a8a8-d924c20d5e74", "fax": null, "name": "若草山餵鹿體驗", "tags": null, "type": "experience", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/b354e0f5-883d-4860-a8a8-d924c20d5e74-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/b354e0f5-883d-4860-a8a8-d924c20d5e74-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "nara", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 34.6845445, "is_active": true, "longitude": 135.8048359, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:49:06.924809+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "奈良若草山餵鹿體驗，奈良公園若草山的野生鹿群，可買鹿仙貝餵食。鹿會鞠躬要食物，可愛又療癒。春季可登若草山看全景。這是奈良必體驗活動，也是親子旅遊首選。鹿仙貝200日圓/束，建議預留1-2小時。可搭配東大寺、春日大社一起遊覽。需注意鹿會頂人或咬衣服。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Nara Deer Feeding", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "b363d4c3-bef5-4150-b053-53266e940c95", "fax": null, "name": "邦勞島白沙灘", "tags": ["海灘", "潛水", "跳島", "度假"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "長灘島最著名的4公里白色粉狀沙灘，被譽為亞洲最美海灘之一。分為S1-S3三個區域，S1最細緻也最商業化，適合各種水上活動。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "boracay", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 11.9674, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.9248, "region_id": null, "country_id": "philippines", "created_at": "2025-10-28T10:22:46.629499+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "薄荷島邦勞白沙灘，邦勞島南岸的白沙灘，比阿羅娜海灘更安靜、更長。可游泳、浮潛、日光浴、吃海鮮。BoholBeachClub、SouthPalmsResort都在這裡。免費參觀，", "contac