，登別山上的棕熊保護區，纜車登山、可看100多隻棕熊、餵食體驗、熊博物館。棕熊會揮手要食物，可愛又療癒。這是登別必訪景點，也是親子旅遊首選。門票2,800日圓，建議預留2-3小時。可搭配登別溫泉、地獄谷一起遊覽。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Noboribetsu Bear Park", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 2, "opening_hours": {"daily": "10:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 150}, {"id": "b3fe27c8-88d7-4a25-bb60-18e10927ce4c", "fax": null, "name": "IT Park", "tags": null, "type": "shopping", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "bohol", "website": null, "category": "主題樂園 / Theme Park", "latitude": 10.3307983, "is_active": true, "longitude": 123.9068258, "region_id": null, "country_id": "philippines", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:26:58.916058+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "IT Park Cebu，宿霧科技園區，也是夜生活與美食區。餐廳、酒吧、咖啡廳、按摩店林立，24小時營業。The Pyramid、Sugbo Mercado 夜市都在這裡。這是宿霧必訪景點，也是夜生活中心。免費參觀，建議晚上前往。可搭配 Ayala Center 一起遊覽。安全、乾淨、現代化。烤乳豬、海鮮BBQ都能吃到。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "PH", "english_name": "IT Park", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "b40a493a-82ef-465c-9a88-0a7c25745ce3", "fax": null, "name": "神農街", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "台南市中西區神農街", "city_id": "tainan-35ba0392-8bed-40b6-b7af-706ea6be60a5", "website": null, "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": 22.9985, "is_active": true, "longitude": 120.196, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-01-09T03:31:23.908376+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "update