"japan", "created_at": "2026-01-23T00:38:30.671089+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "東京晴空塔，高634公尺，日本最高建築。350公尺天望デッキ和450公尺天望回廊兩個觀景台，360度俯瞰東京。天氣好時能看到富士山。購物商場Solamachi有300家商店、水族館、天文館。夜晚塔身點燈，「雅」和「粋」交替。這是東京新地標，也是看東京夜景的最佳地點。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Tokyo Skytree", "ticket_price": "350m觀景台平日2100日圓、假日2300日圓，450m追加1000-1100日圓", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 2, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-22:00（最後入場21:00）"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "b4514df8-9320-4afd-af6e-1c64ceee4437", "fax": null, "name": "廣島和平紀念資料館", "tags": null, "type": "museum", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/b4514df8-9320-4afd-af6e-1c64ceee4437-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/b4514df8-9320-4afd-af6e-1c64ceee4437-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "hiroshima", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 34.3915495, "is_active": true, "longitude": 132.4530979, "region_id": "jp_chugoku", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:55:41.265286+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "廣島和平紀念資料館，展示1945年原子彈轟炸歷史的博物館。被爆者遺物、照片、影片、證言，呈現原爆的殘酷與和平的珍貴。2019年重新開幕，展示更加震撼。這是認識原爆歷史、反思戰爭的重要場所，也是廣島必訪景點。門票200日圓，建議預留1-2小時。位於和平紀念公園內，可搭配原爆圓頂館一起參觀。氛圍沉重，需有心理準備。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Hiroshima Peace Memorial Museum", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "dura