"依官網而定", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"open": "09:00", "close": "17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "babb0cd4-f719-4eb4-baf6-c460eb54e475", "fax": null, "name": "金山寺", "tags": ["山丘寺廟", "佛塔", "舊城視野"], "type": "temple", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "bangkok", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 13.7538418, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.5066951, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:37.910025+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《金山寺》Wat Saket 坐落在人造山丘頂端,是曼谷少數需要爬坡才能抵達的寺廟。344 級階梯兩側是菩提樹與小佛龕,每一級都承載著朝聖者的祈願。山頂的金色佛塔在陽光下反射刺眼的光芒,塔內供奉著佛陀的舍利。站在觀景台上,整個舊城區的紅色屋頂與金色尖塔盡收眼底,現代高樓在遠方形成灰色輪廓。這裡沒有大皇宮的華麗,沒有臥佛寺的壯觀,只有高度帶來的視野與爬坡後的寧靜。每年十一月的水燈節,金山寺會點亮千盞蠟燭,成為曼谷最美的宗教景觀。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Wat Saket", "ticket_price": "成人100-200泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "bac659d3-24a0-4c42-aad4-a3d39aa8cdf4", "fax": null, "name": "砂之美術館", "tags": ["藝術", "博物館", "砂雕", "獨特"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "全球唯一室內沙雕美術館，每年更換主題，展示世界級沙雕作品", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/bac659d3-24a0-4c42-aad4-a3d39aa8cdf4-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/bac659d3-24a0-4c42-aad4-a3d39aa8cdf4-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "tottori", "website": "https://www.sand-museum.jp/", "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 35.538, "is_active": true, "longitude": 134.231, "region_id": "jp_c