\n旅遊提示：可以買人蔘茶或韓方護膚品當伴手禮", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "daegu", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 35.8714, "is_active": true, "longitude": 128.6014, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:01:17.876298+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "大邱藥令市，韓國最大的韓藥材市場，400多年歷史。人蔘、鹿茸、靈芝、藥材應有盡有。可參觀韓醫藥博物館、體驗韓藥足浴、購買韓方化妝品。這是大邱必訪景點，也是認識韓醫文化的好地方。免費參觀，建議預留2-3小時。每年10月舉辦藥令市韓方文化節。可搭配西門市場、大邱近代歷史館一起遊覽。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "Daegu Yangnyeongsi", "ticket_price": "依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 52, "opening_hours": {"daily": "11:00-22:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "bd57c14b-176f-41c8-9da5-a40c9a5f05ae", "fax": null, "name": "雙龍寺", "tags": ["雙龍", "佛舍利", "朝聖"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "清邁最神聖的佛寺，金碧輝煌。搭纜車或爬306階樓梯上山。門票50泰銖。可俯瞰清邁全景。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 18.8048, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.9218, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-11-01T10:48:49.788154+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《雙龍寺》是素帖寺的別稱,因階梯兩側的雙龍那伽雕塑而得名。這座寺廟建於1383年,傳說是由白象馱著佛舍利找到的建寺位置。金色佛塔內供奉佛陀舍利,是泰北最重要的朝聖地。寺廟平台可俯瞰整座清邁城,視野遼闊,清晨時分雲霧繚繞,午後則陽光燦爛。建議傍晚前往,夕陽將城市染成金色,夜幕降臨後萬家燈火逐一亮起。這裡不只是觀光景點,更是清邁人的精神象徵——每個在地人一生至少會來朝聖一次。尊重宗教空間,穿著需遮肩蓋膝。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Wat Phra That Doi Suthep", "ticket_price": "成人30泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "06:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "bd5c67ed-53ff-4393-a790-c3d9aa0a5b42", "fax": null, "name": "玉佛寺", "tags": ["寺廟", "翡翠佛", "神聖"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "位於大皇宮內，供奉翡翠玉佛。泰國最神聖的佛寺。門票含在大皇宮套票內。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/bd5c67ed-53ff-4393-a790-c3d9aa0a5b42-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/bd5c67ed-53ff-4393-a790-c3d9aa0a5b42-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "bangkok", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 13.7517, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.4927, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-11-01T10:48:49.473797+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《玉佛寺》位於大皇宮範圍內,供奉高 66 公分的翡翠佛像,是泰國最神聖的宗教場所。金碧輝煌的建築群以細膩的馬賽克與金箔裝飾,在陽光下閃耀刺目。迴廊壁畫描繪《羅摩衍那》史詩,歷經修復但仍保有原始構圖。遊客需著長褲與遮肩上衣,赤腳進入主殿。這裡的莊嚴不來自寧靜,而是視覺的壓倒性——色彩、光線與宗教符號的密集排列,形成某種神聖的過載狀態。清晨或傍晚前往可避開人潮,更能感受空間本身的力量。這是理解泰國王權與佛教關係的核心場域。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Wat Phra Kaew", "ticket_price": "成人100-200泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "bd644e70-edf0-4927-8d31-8e9a7670ee32", "fax": null, "name": "上海灘頂級旗袍大師私人訂製", "tags": ["工藝體驗", "頂級體驗"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "頂級體驗 | 工藝體驗 | 價位: | 難度:easy", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "shanghai", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "country_id": "china", "created_at": "2026-04-06T22:24:03.089193+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "跟隨國家級非物質文化遺產傳承人，學習旗袍的歷史、裁剪與刺繡技藝。親自挑選絲綢布料，量身訂製專屬旗袍。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "CN", "english_name": "Shanghai Master Qipao Tailoring Experience", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 0}, {"id": "bd8f9186-00bd-4aae-b20e-daaa1707ce40", "fax": null, "name": "南奔哈里奔猜寺", "tags": ["古寺", "南奔", "金塔"], "type": "temple", "notes": "清邁周邊的千年古寺，蘭納建築的傑作。46米高的金塔是北泰最古老的佛塔，每年有盛大的祭典。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/bd8f9186-00bd-4aae-b20e-daaa1707ce40-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/bd8f9186-00bd-4aae-b20e-daaa1707ce40-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 18.5761, "is_active": true, "longitude": 99.0022, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-16T06:49:14.5286+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《南奔哈里奔猜寺》位於清邁南方約30公里的南奔古城，是泰北最古老的寺廟之一。金色佛塔在陽光下反射刺眼光芒，塔身鑲嵌的銅片隨風輕響。這裡遊客稀少，多是在地信眾前來參拜，氛圍寧靜虔誠。寺內的木雕迴廊保存了數百年歷史，雕工細膩到讓人屏息。與清邁市區寺廟的觀光化不同，這裡保留了宗教空間該有的肅穆感。建議清晨前往，晨光穿過菩提樹葉灑在佛塔上的瞬間，你會理解為什麼泰國人稱寺廟為「心的避難所」。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Wat Phra That Hariphunchai", "ticket_price": "成人100-200泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 425, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "bda7b533-c2bf-4aec-9cf7-83349cf34ddb", "fax": null, "name": "茵他儂國家公園", "tags": ["國家公園", "高山", "健行"], "type": "park", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/bda7b533-c2bf-4aec-9cf7-83349cf34ddb-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/bda7b533-c2bf-4aec-9cf7-83349cf34ddb-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 18.5884834, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.4874637, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:24:39.971611+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《茵他儂國家公園》擁有泰國最高峰，海拔2565公尺的茵他儂山。山頂終年涼爽，清晨時分霧氣瀰漫，能見度不足十公尺。公園內的 Kew Mae Pan 步道穿越雲霧森林，苔蘚覆蓋的樹幹與蕨類植物構成魔幻場景。這裡的生態系統與清邁平原完全不同——溫帶植物、候鳥棲息地、少數民族村落。Twin Royal Pagodas 是為泰皇與皇后建造的雙塔，視野遼闊但常被雲霧籠罩。從清邁市區開車約兩小時，山路蜿蜒但路況良好。帶件外套，山上氣溫可能只有10度。這是清邁的另一個維度——不是寺廟與夜市，而是自然與高度。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Doi Inthanon", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "be7c3bc4-1d59-4703-ad8a-22e2370bc083", "fax": null, "name": "新天地", "tags": ["時尚", "購物", "餐廳"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "上海時尚地標，石庫門建築改建的高端商圈和餐飲區", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": "https://www.xintiandi.com/", "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": 31.22, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.469, "region_id": "cn_east", "country_id": "china", "created_at": "2025-11-01T10:48:50.642099+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "新天地，中國知名景點，值得探訪。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "CN", "english_name": "Xintiandi", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_v