ated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《青森睡魔之家》位於青森車站旁，是體驗青森睡魔祭精髓的最佳場所。館內常設展示5座巨型睡魔燈籠，高達9公尺的武者人形在燈光照射下栩栩如生，氣勢磅礴。透過影片與互動展示，遊客可了解睡魔祭的歷史、製作工藝、祭典熱鬧場景。二樓設有手作體驗區，可親手繪製迷你睡魔面具。夏季睡魔祭期間，館外廣場舉辦祭典活動，遊客可穿著浴衣參與「跳人」(Haneto) 舞蹈，感受東北夏日祭典的狂熱氛圍。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Nebuta Museum Wa Rasse", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "c34adedb-aab0-45e1-8fa3-b96e02b90406", "fax": null, "name": "上野東照宮", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://wzvwmawpkapcmkfmkvav.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/resources/attractions/c34adedb-aab0-45e1-8fa3-b96e02b90406/1775722463602_m7ah1rw2kat.jpg"], "address": "", "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-04-09T08:06:03.959001+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "上野東照宮是位於東京上野恩賜公園內的一座華麗神社，始建於 1627 年，現存的主要建築為 1651 年由第三代將軍德川家光重建而成。它是少數完整躲過上野戰爭、關東大地震及二戰空襲，並將江戶時代初期建築原貌完整保留至今的歷史古蹟，被列為日本國家重要文化財。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "c360e5fd-74b5-4a85-ad95-2816e19774fa", "fax": null, "name": "獅子林", "tags": null, "type": "garden", "notes": "蘇州四大名園之一，以假山迷宮著稱。獅子形狀的太湖石是特色，乾隆皇帝曾六度到訪。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 31.325, "is_active": true, "longitu