ame": "咖啡公寓", "tags": ["咖啡館", "文創", "垂直街區"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "ho-chi-minh", "website": null, "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "created_at": "2026-04-04T11:19:44.822+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《咖啡公寓》將舊公寓改造成垂直咖啡街,九層樓每層都是不同風格的咖啡館。從復古工業風、極簡北歐、到熱帶雨林主題,每家店都有自己的性格。搭電梯上樓,隨意推開一扇門,也許會發現你最喜歡的角落。這裡是胡志明年輕世代的社交空間——帶筆電工作的數位遊牧者、拍照打卡的網紅、約會的情侶。建築本身不新,但正因舊才有改造的趣味。週末人潮擁擠,平日下午來最舒適。咖啡公寓證明:創意不需要新建築,舊空間也能有新生命。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "The Cafe Apartment", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "c61a8b2a-df5f-4754-8060-09c40e4e9529", "fax": null, "name": "千疊敷", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/c61a8b2a-df5f-4754-8060-09c40e4e9529-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/c61a8b2a-df5f-4754-8060-09c40e4e9529-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "wakayama", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 33.68, "is_active": true, "longitude": 135.345, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-01-23T02:48:43.171256+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "和歌山千疊敷，白濱南部的海蝕平台，面積約4公頃。如千張塌塌米鋪開，故名千疊敷。海浪長年侵蝕形成平坦岩盤、潮池，景觀獨特。夕陽西下時，海面染成金紅色，浪漫至極。這是白濱代表景點，也是看夕陽的好地方。注意安全，勿越過護欄。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Senjojiki", "ticket_p