 "description": "寧平碧洞，意為「碧綠的洞穴」，建於15世紀的佛寺洞穴。三層寺廟依山而建：下洞、中洞、上洞，需爬石階而上。洞內供奉佛像，鐘乳石、石筍自然形成。登上山頂，俯瞰寧平田園風光，喀斯特峰林與稻田交織。這是寧平最美的寺廟洞穴，也是攝影愛好者天堂。免費參觀，", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "免費（自由捐獻）", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"notes": "全年開放，建議避開中午炎熱時段", "regular": {"open": "06:00", "close": "18:00"}}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "cab6d834-10df-46ab-923d-b91f36cfef32", "fax": null, "name": "帕禪寺", "tags": ["古寺", "蘭納", "木造"], "type": "temple", "notes": "清邁歷史最悠久的寺廟之一，蘭納建築的代表。金塔和木雕精美，週日市集從這裡延伸至古城門。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/cab6d834-10df-46ab-923d-b91f36cfef32-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/cab6d834-10df-46ab-923d-b91f36cfef32-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 18.7872, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.9889, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-16T06:49:14.922856+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《帕禪寺》Wat Phra Kaew Don Tao 位於清邁古城北側，曾供奉過曼谷玉佛寺的翡翠佛像。寺內的蘭納式木造佛殿保存完整，柚木立柱與雕花屋簷經過數百年依然穩固。這裡遊客不多，多是在地信眾前來參拜，氛圍安靜虔誠。佛殿內的壁畫描繪佛陀生平，顏色雖已褪色但構圖精美。寺廟後方有座小型博物館，展示蘭納王朝的宗教文物與古籍。清晨或傍晚前往最合適，陽光斜射進佛殿時，金色佛像在光影中顯得格外莊嚴。這是清邁少數還保有宗教空間肅穆感的寺廟。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Wat Phra Kaew Don Tao", "ticket_price": "成人100-200泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 337, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 45}, {"id": "cad58892-6b51-4181-afad-752be347e844", "fax": null, "name"