 價位: | 難度:None", "phone": null, "images": ["https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559827260-dc66d52bef19?w=800", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578683010236-d716f9a3f461?w=800"], "address": null, "city_id": "busan", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2026-04-06T22:24:11.198497+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "探索濟州島令人屏息的海岸線，結合UNESCO認證的海女（Haenyeo）文化體驗。徒步濟州偶來小路（Olle Trail）最美的海岸段，欣賞玄武岩海岸、柱狀節理、藍色海蝕洞。午餐與真正的海女阿嬤共餐，品嚐她們親自潛水採集的海鮮：鮑魚、海膽、海參、海藻。聆聽海女的生命故事與傳統技藝。下午參觀城山日出峰，體驗簡單的自由潛水訓練。傍晚入住濟州頂級度假村，享受火山石桑拿與海景溫泉。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "Jeju Island Coastal Trekking & Haenyeo Culture", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 0}, {"id": "cd5d7eb6-1722-4e90-afd1-a07d59e51f84", "fax": null, "name": "燕子口", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "花蓮縣秀林鄉中橫公路", "city_id": "769364e9-d3e2-474f-bc80-0184c00e6d9e", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 24.1753, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.5406, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-01-09T03:36:28.944514+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "花蓮新城太魯閣國家公園內的步道，立霧溪切割大理石形成的峽谷。燕子在峭壁間築巢，因而得名。步道狹窄，需戴安全帽行走。峽谷兩側峭壁高聳，抬頭只見一線天。這是太魯閣最經典的景觀之一。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": "Swallow Grotto", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 35, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:30-16