"english_name": "Nha Trang Yoga", "ticket_price": null, "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "d4ba217b-c79f-46c3-8786-99afe2f91290", "fax": null, "name": "川山瀑布", "tags": ["瀑布", "天然泳池", "自然", "健行", "清涼"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "即Kawasan Falls，宿霧最著名的瀑布。分多層，每層都有天然泳池。碧綠色的水質清澈見底。可在瀑布下按摩（水柱SPA）。\n\n旅遊提示：建議安排半天，可慢慢玩每一層", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "bohol", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 9.8698, "is_active": true, "longitude": 123.502, "region_id": null, "country_id": "philippines", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:26:58.219073+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "薄荷島川山瀑布，薄荷島隱藏版瀑布，三層瀑布、翡翠綠潭水，景色壯觀。需徒步約30分鐘進入，冒險感十足。這是薄荷島秘境，也是避開人潮的好選擇。需穿可弄濕的鞋、帶泳衣。當地導遊推薦。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "PH", "english_name": "Kawasan Falls", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "d4d71399-99c9-4a26-bf5c-e9d2f9c97356", "fax": null, "name": "瑪黑區", "tags": ["古區", "猶太區", "潮流", "美食", "巴黎"], "type": "shopping", "notes": "巴黎最古老的街區之一，混合猶太文化和時尚潮流。有許多精品店、藝廊、餐廳。週日也營業（巴黎少數）。Falafel是必吃美食。\n\n旅遊提示：L As du Fallafel是最有名的口袋餅店", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "購物 / Shopping", "latitude": 48.8603823, "is_active": true, "longitude": 2.360742, "region_id": "ile-de-france", "country_id": "france", "created_at": "2025-12-06T06:49:56.22071+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "瑪黑區，法國巴黎著名景點，展現藝術與文化之都魅力。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "FR", "english_name": "Le Marais", "ticket_price": "依官網而定", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 750, "opening_hours": {"open": "00:00", "close": "24:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "d4dad010-d6b6-427c-b1a9-f9bd912c8117", "fax": null, "name": "濱海灣花園", "tags": ["花園", "超級樹", "溫室", "燈光秀", "新加坡"], "type": "garden", "notes": "新加坡最美的城市花園，有18棵高25-50公尺的超級樹。每晚有免費燈光秀（19:45和20:45）。雲霧林和花穹是付費溫室，很值得參觀。\n\n旅遊提示：傍晚來看日落和燈光秀最佳", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 1.2816, "is_active": true, "longitude": 103.8636, "region_id": null, "country_id": "singapore", "created_at": "2025-12-06T02:06:36.205609+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "新加坡濱海灣花園，未來主義的城市花園。超級樹Grove高25-50公尺，夜晚燈光秀配合音樂，科技與自然完美結合。雲霧林、花穹兩座冷室，展示世界各地植物。空中步道OCBCSkyway連接超級樹，從高處俯瞰整個花園。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "SG", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "冷室成人SGD 28，空中步道SGD 14", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 822, "opening_hours": {"daily": "戶外花園05:00-02:00，冷室09:00-21:00", "light_show": "每晚19:45、20:45"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "d518b105-8255-45e6-9121-e5de55dcef6b", "fax": null, "name": "契迪龍寺", "tags": ["古寺", "廢墟", "歷史"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/d518b105-8255-45e6-9121-e5de55dcef6b-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/d518b105-8255-45e6-9121-e5de55dcef6b-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 18.7883, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.9853, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-10-28T06:44:14.118901+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《契迪龍寺》不是清邁最華麗的寺廟，但站在那座半毀的佛塔前，你會感受到時間的重量。1545年的地震讓塔尖崩落，至今沒有修復，因為殘缺本身就是歷史。佛塔四面各有巨型象頭支撐塔身，經過五百年風雨，象鼻已模糊但氣勢依然。清晨六點，僧侶托鉢經過，赤腳踩在石板路上的聲音，比任何導覽都更真實。寺內有棵五百年的菩提樹，樹根盤踞地面如龍爪。黃昏時分，夕陽將塔身染成金色，遊客散去後的寧靜，才是這座寺廟本來的樣子。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Wat Chedi Luang", "ticket_price": "成人100-200泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 5, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "d529f95b-db7c-47dc-857d-30aaa6b8bc4a", "fax": null, "name": "天上山纜車", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/d529f95b-db7c-47dc-857d-30aaa6b8bc4a-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/d529f95b-db7c-47dc-857d-30aaa6b8bc4a-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "ebe380fc-1d8f-4555-8272-f3876f41b58b", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 35.50378, "is_active": true, "longitude": 138.7744071, "region_id": "jp_kanto", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-02-05T00:11:28.490735+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "天上山纜車連接河口湖畔與天上山公園，搭乘纜車約3分鐘即可抵達山頂。在山頂可以欣賞富士山與河口湖的絕美全景，是河口湖地區最受歡迎的觀景點之一。山頂還有兔子神社，傳說兔子是這座山的守護神。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Mt. Tenjo Ropeway", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_ord