海的壯麗景觀。橋塔高297公尺，可搭乘導覽行程登上主塔眺望瀨戶內海與明石海峽。夜間點燈變化繽紛，是神戶港夜景重要元素。周邊有舞子海上散步道、孫文紀念館。從神戶或淡路島眺望大橋，日出日落皆美。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Akashi Kaikyo Bridge", "ticket_price": "通行免費，主塔參觀3300日圓", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 346, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天通行"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "d91f4efa-29a0-4acf-bffd-a01d281e0ca0", "fax": null, "name": "蘭卡威纜車", "tags": ["纜車", "觀景", "天空之橋", "蘭卡威", "地標"], "type": "viewpoint", "notes": "東南亞最長的纜車之一，全長2.2公里，從山腳到660公尺高山頂。中途站和山頂站都有觀景台。天空之橋就在山頂站。\n\n旅遊提示：套票含纜車和天空之橋較划算", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "langkawi", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 6.35, "is_active": true, "longitude": 99.8, "region_id": null, "country_id": "malaysia", "created_at": "2025-12-06T02:06:45.929326+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "蘭卡威纜車，蘭卡威必訪景點，從東方村搭纜車到GunungMatCincang山頂。2.2公里纜車，分3段，中途有SkyBridge天空之橋。山頂可360度俯瞰蘭卡威、安達曼海、泰國邊境。這是蘭卡威最熱門景點，也是看全島的最佳角度。纜車來回票85馬幣。建議早上前往，能見度較高。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "MY", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 875, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "d97a1715-5a0c-4b92-89ec-7601b926a589", "fax": null, "name": "醍醐寺", "tags": ["櫻花", "世界遺產", "五重塔"], "type": "temple", "notes": "豐臣秀吉舉辦醍醐花見的賞櫻名所，五重塔是京都最古老建築。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/d97a1715-5a0c-4b92-89ec-7601b926a589-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/d97a1715-5a0c-4b92-89ec-7601b926a589-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "kyoto", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 34.9511, "is_active": true, "longitude": 135.8217, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-06T06:57:29.587641+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "京都世界文化遺產，真言宗醍醐派總本山，創建於874年。以春季櫻花聞名，豐臣秀吉曾在此舉辦「醍醐賞花」盛會。三寶院庭園是國家特別名勝，五重塔是京都最古老木造建築。境內分上下醍醐，步行登山需2小時。秋季紅葉與靈寶館藏豐富佛教文物，是京都重要佛教文化景點。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Daigo-ji", "ticket_price": "三寶院‧靈寶館1000日圓", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 805, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "d9a3dea3-6e9f-46a9-bbf2-9fbfcd101219", "fax": null, "name": "倫敦塔橋", "tags": ["大橋", "地標", "維多利亞", "開橋", "倫敦"], "type": "heritage", "notes": "倫敦最具代表性的大橋，1894年建成的維多利亞式建築。可購票參觀塔橋展覽和玻璃步道。每天有幾次開橋讓大船通過。\n\n旅遊提示：官網有開橋時刻表，可提前查詢", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "地標建築 / Landmark", "latitude": 51.5081, "is_active": true, "longitude": -0.0759, "region_id": null, "country_id": "uk", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:06:39.169661+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "倫敦塔，英國歷史堡壘，建於1066年。曾是皇宮、監獄、刑場。守塔烏鴉、王冠珠寶、血腥歷史，每個角落都有故事。UNESCO世界文化遺產。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "GB", "english_name": "Tower Bridge", "ticket_price": "成人£25-30", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 492, "opening_hours": {"open": "09:30", "close": "18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "d9c9d29e-0dc4-49a8-962c-e188ca906624", "fax": null, "name": "灕江", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes":