石佛需要排隊，週末人多", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "daegu", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 35.9772, "is_active": true, "longitude": 128.6925, "region_id": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:01:17.577774+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "大邱八公山，大邱近郊的名山，海拔1192公尺。有桐華寺、銀海寺等古剎，登山步道完善。春天櫻花、秋天楓紅，四季景觀各異。山頂可俯瞰大邱市區。這是大邱人週末登山的好去處，也是認識大邱自然景觀的窗口。有纜車可搭乘，也可步行登山。周邊有溫泉、度假村，可以泡湯休憩。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "Palgongsan Mountain", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 16, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "d9e4264f-591e-43bc-8fd6-d4de9b78078b", "fax": null, "name": "格蘭島", "tags": ["海島", "水上活動", "浮潛", "熱鬧"], "type": "beach", "notes": "從芭達雅搭船30分鐘即達。水比芭達雅海灘清澈很多。有水上活動。船票約200泰銖來回。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/d9e4264f-591e-43bc-8fd6-d4de9b78078b-1.jpg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/d9e4264f-591e-43bc-8fd6-d4de9b78078b-2.jpg"], "address": null, "city_id": "pattaya", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 12.9174502, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.7782008, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:55:51.254684+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《格蘭島》又稱珊瑚島，是芭達雅外海最熱門的一日遊目的地。快艇15分鐘即達，島上有塔威恩、桑灣、天恩等多個海灘，各具特色。水上活動項目豐富：拖曳傘、香蕉船、海底漫步、浮潛看珊瑚。島上餐廳提供新鮮海鮮，可邊用餐邊看海。相較沙美島更熱鬧，適合喜愛水上刺激活動的遊客。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Koh Larn", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 360}, {"id": "d9ff7f4a-1631-4d8f-a9e5-7031192f7872", "fax": null, "name": "三仙台", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "台東縣成功鎮三仙里基翬路74號", "city_id": "02d6cb3c-b3d0-40c7-b283-d2d5f446ba1d", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 23.1236, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.4089, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-01-09T03:36:28.944514+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "三根醒目的巨柱矗立在水面上，退潮時可以走到岩石上，漲潮時三仙台成為海中小島。傳說八仙中的呂洞賓、李鐵拐、何仙姑曾登臨此地，因而得名。拱橋連接陸地與小島，走過八拱橋，登上小島，360度的海景盡收眼底。這是台東最具代表性的地標。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": "Sanxiantai", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 41, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:30-17:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "da056c09-05ad-4823-94d7-5794d53b8f7d", "fax": null, "name": "川村子之文アイヌ記念館", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/da056c09-05ad-4823-94d7-5794d53b8f7d-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/da056c09-05ad-4823-94d7-5794d53b8f7d-2.jpg"], "address": null, "city_id": "asahikawa", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 43.775, "is_active": true, "longitude": 142.3833, "region_id": "jp_hokkaido", "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-01-23T02:48:47.12784+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+