y": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 25.0372, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.4999, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-01-09T03:31:23.908376+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "台北萬華龍山寺,建於1738年,是台北三大廟門之一,也是香火最鼎盛的廟宇。主祀觀世音菩薩,配祀媽祖、文昌帝君、關聖帝君等眾神。精緻的木雕、石雕、剪黏、彩繪,展現傳統廟宇建築藝術極致。前殿、正殿、後殿格局完整,銅鑄龍柱、螺旋藻井都是藝術瑰寶。這裡不只是宗教場所,更是台北歷史、庶民信仰與社區文化的重要據點。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": "Longshan Temple", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 4, "opening_hours": {"daily": "06:00-22:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 45}, {"id": "dd881c57-66ce-4f4f-960f-fee6f3bc5238", "fax": null, "name": "台北101", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "台北市信義區信義路五段7號", "city_id": "36e5e6b9-03c4-467e-b14a-0e5bbab0b3df", "website": "https://www.taipei-101.com.tw/", "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 25.0339, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.5645, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-01-09T03:31:23.908376+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "台灣最高的觀景大樓，101層樓高508公尺。89樓是觀景台，360度俯瞰台北，天氣好時可以看到淡水、基隆。跨年煙火從這裡發射，是台北地標。B1美食街、購物商場，這裡不只是觀景，更是台北現代化的象徵。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "english_name": "Taipei 101", "ticket_price": "觀景台全票600元", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 1, "opening_hours": {"daily": "觀景台11:00-21:00，購物中心11:00-21:30"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 120}, {"id": "dd904aa6-3f91-44ca-bb39-59a0ffc72069", "fax": null, "name": "華欣老街", "tags": ["老街", "傳統", "在地"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "保留傳統泰式建築和在地生活氛圍的舊城區", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/dd904aa6-3f91-44ca-bb39-59a0ffc72069-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/dd904aa6-3f91-44ca-bb39-59a0ffc72069-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 12.572, "is_active": true, "longitude": 99.952, "region_id": "th_central", "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2026-03-17T03:14:01.620413+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "華欣老街，華欣市區傳統老街區，Petchkasem Road、Chomsin Road、Naresdamri Road保存完整的老建築。復古咖啡廳、文創店、古董店、華欣藝術村。這是華欣文青景點，也是認識在地文化的好地方。免費參觀，建議預留1-2小時。可搭配華欣火車站、華欣夜市一起遊覽。週末有創意市集。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Hua Hin Old Town (Soi 51)", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 60}, {"id": "ddc8505a-a914-4e61-8b1f-504098480989", "fax": null, "name": "陽明山國家公園", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "台北市北投區竹子湖路1-20號", "city_id": "36e5e6b9-03c4-467e-b14a-0e5bbab0b3df", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 25.1693, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.5601, "region_id": null, "country_id": "taiwan-country-001", "created_at": "2026-01-09T03:31:23.908376+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "台北陽明山國家公園，台灣第三座國家公園。火山地形、溫泉、櫻花、芒花、箭竹林,四季景色不同。春天賞櫻賞杜鵑，夏天避暑健行，秋天看芒花，冬天泡溫泉。擎天崗草原、小油坑硫磺噴氣孔、陽明書屋、冷水坑，每個景點都有特色。這是台北人的後花園，也是認識台灣火山地質的最佳教室。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TW", "en