-17T03:15:31.816252+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "峴港大教堂，峴港市中心的粉紅色教堂，建於1923年。法國哥德式建築，粉紅色外牆、彩色玻璃窗、尖塔，充滿童話氣息。教堂內部簡約，祭壇、聖像莊嚴。這是峴港最上鏡的建築，也是Instagram熱門打卡點。周邊有HanMarket、龍橋，可以串聯遊覽。建議早上或傍晚前來，光線最美。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "VN", "english_name": "Da Nang Cathedral", "ticket_price": "免費", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 30}, {"id": "e174df8f-61a7-4d64-8fe7-91dc95b02207", "fax": null, "name": "臥佛寺", "tags": ["臥佛", "泰式按摩", "宗教文化"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "46公尺金色臥佛必看。可體驗正宗泰式按摩。門票200泰銖。與大皇宮相鄰可一起參觀。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/e174df8f-61a7-4d64-8fe7-91dc95b02207-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/e174df8f-61a7-4d64-8fe7-91dc95b02207-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "bangkok", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 13.7465, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.4928, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-10-27T15:26:40.818404+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《臥佛寺》Wat Pho 的主角是一尊長 46 公尺的鍍金臥佛,佛陀側臥的姿態象徵涅槃。腳底鑲嵌 108 個貝殼圖案,每一個都代表佛陀的不同特徵。寺廟內有超過一千尊佛像,數量多到讓人目不暇給。這裡也是泰式按摩的發源地,寺內設有按摩學校,牆上刻著經絡圖與按摩手法。遊客可以在寺廟內體驗傳統按摩,價格親民,手法正宗,師傅的力道大到讓你懷疑這是療癒還是修行。臥佛寺不只是觀光景點,更是泰國醫學與宗教文化的活教材。這是曼谷最具知識深度的寺廟。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Wat Pho", "ticket_price": "成人200泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 2, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:00-18:30"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": 