-d1e24185ccfc", "fax": null, "name": "夜間動物園", "tags": ["夜間動物園", "遊園車", "親子"], "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/e4299dfc-f9a7-457d-ab72-d1e24185ccfc-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/e4299dfc-f9a7-457d-ab72-d1e24185ccfc-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "活動體驗 / Activity", "latitude": 18.7384735, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.9165453, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-10-28T06:44:14.79691+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《夜間動物園》Chiang Mai Night Safari 與清邁夜間動物園為同一地點,位於素帖山腳佔地120公頃。遊園車分草食區與肉食區兩條路線,在夜間燈光照射下觀察動物的自然行為。長頸鹿會伸長脖子靠近車窗,斑馬群在月光下奔跑,老虎在夜間更活躍。園區內有音樂噴泉表演,但動物本身比人造景觀更值得關注。適合帶孩子來,但請尊重動物——不拍打玻璃、不餵食、不開閃光燈。夜間動物園的意義在於理解:許多動物在夜晚才展現真實面貌,白天看到的只是牠們睡覺的樣子。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Chiang Mai Night Safari", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 9, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 240}, {"id": "e45baec7-a1ab-4cf5-9524-2b11c56217a1", "fax": null, "name": "雙廊古鎮", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 25.6074778, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.2651597, "region_id": null, "country_id": "china", "created_at": "2025-12-06T02:12:13.408703+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "雙廊古鎮，中國保存完整的傳統古鎮，展現古代江南水鄉或古城生活樣貌。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "CN", "en