07+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《水上市場》作為體驗項目,通常指安帕瓦或丹嫩莎朵等地的半日遊行程。清晨搭乘長尾船穿梭水道,兩岸椰林與高腳屋構成熱帶風景。船家販售現切水果、椰子冰淇淋與炭烤海鮮,價格已觀光化但仍保有手作溫度。較佳的體驗方式是避開週末人潮,選擇平日清晨,當晨霧尚未散去,船槳劃水聲與鳥鳴交織。這不是未經觸碰的原始場景,而是觀光與傳統生活方式的協商結果。接受其表演性,同時捕捉那些未被完全格式化的瞬間,是參與的正確態度。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Damnoen Saduak Floating Market", "ticket_price": "免費（船遊約200-400泰銖）", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 78, "opening_hours": {"daily": "06:00-12:00，最佳時間07:00-09:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 150}, {"id": "ec1c8b82-5e68-4634-a7ae-09564ae2d58e", "fax": null, "name": "直升機島", "tags": null, "type": "attraction", "notes": null, "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "palawan", "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 11.22, "is_active": true, "longitude": 119.42, "region_id": null, "country_id": "philippines", "created_at": "2026-01-24T09:04:18.5258+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "愛妮島直升機島，愛妮島跳島遊景點，島嶼形狀如直升機停機坪。白沙灘、清澈海水、石灰岩峭壁，景色如明信片。可游泳、浮潛、拍照。這是愛妮島必訪景點，也是拍照聖地。包含在 Tour C 跳島遊。建議預留1-2小時。可搭配 Matinloc Shrine、Hidden Beach 一起遊覽。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "PH", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": {"daily": "全天開放"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 180}, {"id": "ec529c6e-7ffb-4293-a391-d796b278c089", "fax": null, "name": "Le Jardin D'Amour花園", "tags": ["花園", "歐式", "拍照", "浪漫"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "巴拿山上的歐式花園，四季鮮花盛開", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "自然風景 / Nature", "latitude": 15.997, "is_active": true, "longitude": 107.999, "region_id": null, "country_id": "vietnam", "