.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "bangkok", "website": null, "category": "景點 / Attraction", "latitude": 13.7563, "is_active": true, "longitude": 100.5018, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T02:12:34.266871+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《曼谷文華東方》自1876年營業至今,是昭披耶河畔最具歷史重量的酒店。作家廳保留了毛姆與康拉德曾下榻的時代氛圍,深色木質傢俱與老照片構成靜謐角落。河景套房的陽台正對往來船隻,日落時河面反光將金色投射進室內。這裡的服務不張揚,卻精準到位,像是訓練有素的芭蕾舞者。下午茶維持英式傳統,但加入了泰式香料的細微調整。不是靠奢華取勝,而是用時間累積的從容感與對細節的執著,定義了何謂經典。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": null, "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 589, "opening_hours": {"daily": "09:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": null}, {"id": "eec3e3bc-ae40-4ca1-8ad2-b4c2ea2070fa", "fax": null, "name": "迪士尼樂園", "tags": null, "type": "theme_park", "notes": "中國大陸首座迪士尼，奇幻童話城堡是全球最高最大的迪士尼城堡。", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 31.1433, "is_active": true, "longitude": 121.6697, "region_id": "cn_east", "country_id": "china", "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:55:55.197904+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "迪士尼樂園，中國知名景點，值得探訪。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "CN", "english_name": "Shanghai Disneyland", "ticket_price": "免費或依業者而異", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 481, "opening_hours": {"daily": "08:30-17:30"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 600}, {"id": "ef3225f5-d621-4d3d-abf8-a4e3994c9424", "fax": null, "name": "素帖寺", "tags": ["山頂寺廟", "金塔", "聖地"], "type": "temple", "notes": "即雙龍寺，因入口有雙龍雕塑得名。位於素帖山上。傍晚可看日落。與蒲屏皇宮可安排半日遊。", "phone": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/ef3225f5-d621-4d3d-abf8-a4e3994c9424-1.jpeg", "https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/ef3225f5-d621-4d3d-abf8-a4e3994c9424-2.jpeg"], "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "歷史文化 / History & Culture", "latitude": 18.8035942, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.9202265, "region_id": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-06T07:11:10.575015+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "《素帖寺》Wat Phra That Doi Suthep 坐落素帖山頂,海拔1676公尺,是清邁最神聖的寺廟。306級階梯兩側是七頭那伽蛇神雕塑,爬到山頂時氣喘吁吁,但轉身看見整座清邁盆地在腳下展開,疲憊瞬間值得。金色佛塔在陽光下閃耀刺眼,信眾順時針繞塔祈福,手持蓮花與香燭。清晨五點前往可避開人潮,晨霧中的佛塔更顯莊嚴。山下有蒲屏皇宮與苗族村落,可安排半日遊。這裡遊客眾多但依然神聖——因為信仰的力量,比觀光的喧囂更強大。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Wat Phra That Doi Suthep", "ticket_price": "成人30泰銖", "workspace_id": "8ef05a74-1f87-48ab-afd3-9bfeb423935d", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 548, "opening_hours": {"daily": "06:00-18:00"}, "deleted_reason": null, "google_maps_url": null, "duration_minutes": 90}, {"id": "ef695cd8-5436-4842-bdb4-bdab35ea5deb", "fax": null, "name": "重慶人民大禮堂", "tags": ["地標", "建築", "夜景", "廣場"], "type": "attraction", "notes": "可與三峽博物館連遊", "phone": null, "images": null, "address": "重慶市渝中區人民路173號", "city_id": null, "website": null, "category": "地標建築 / Landmark", "latitude": 29.5617, "is_active": true, "longitude": 106.55, "region_id": "cn_southwest", "country_id": "china", "created_at": "2025-12-05T14:34:26.42475+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "重慶人民大禮堂，中國知名景點，值得探訪。", "contact_name": null, "country_code": "CN", "english_name": "Chongqing People's Auditorium", "ticket_price": "免費或依業